<theword date='2017-01-01'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 1 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='143' verse='5' id='Ps143v5'>
<text>Men oldingi kunlarni eslayman,
Sening hamma ishlaring haqida o‘ylayman,
Qo‘llaring ijodini xayolimga keltiraman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 142:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='4' verse='20' id='Act4v20'>
<text>Butrus bilan Yuhanno Majlisga shunday javob qaytardilar:
Biz ko‘rganlarimiz va eshitganlarimiz
to‘g‘risida gapirmasdan tura olmaymiz.</text>
<ref>Havoriylar 4:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-02'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 2 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='6' verse='41' id='L6v41'>
<text>Nima uchun sen birodaringning ko‘zidagi
zirapchani ko‘rasan–u,
o‘z ko‘zingdagi xodani sezmaysan?</text>
<ref>Luqo 6:41</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='12' id='Mt6v12'>
<text>Bizga qarshi gunoh qilganlarni
biz kechirgandek,
Sen ham gunohlarimizni kechirgin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-03'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 3 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='4' verse='29' id='J4v29'>
<text>Yuringlar, bir Odamni ko‘ringlar.
U mening qilgan hamma ishlarimni aytib berdi!
O‘sha Masih emasmikin?</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 4:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='5' verse='8' id='R5v8'>
<text>Biz hali gunohga botgan chog‘imizda,
Masih biz uchun o‘ldi.
Shu yo‘sinda Xudo bizga bo‘lgan
O‘z mehr–muhabbatini namoyon qildi.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 5:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-04'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 4 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='60' chapter='5' verse='5' id='1P5v5'>
<text>Hammangiz, yoshmisiz, qarimisiz, o‘zingizni kamtar tutib,
bir–biringizga xizmat qilinglar.
Zero, Xudo mag‘rurlarga qarshi chiqadi,
kamtarlarga esa inoyat qiladi.</text>
<ref>1 Butrus 5:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='67' id='Ps119v67'>
<text>Jazo olmasimdan oldin adashar edim,
Endi Sening so‘zingga itoat etaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:67</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-05'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 5 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='10' verse='18' id='Dt10v18-19'>
<text>Yetim va bevalarga adolat qiladi,
musofirga mehribonlik qiladi, ularga non va kiyim beradi.
Sizlar ham musofirlarga mehribon bo‘linglar,
o‘zlaringiz ham Misrda musofir edingizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 10:18-19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='38' chapter='7' verse='10' id='Zch7v10'>
<text>Bevalarga, yetimlarga, musofirlarga,
kambag‘allarga zulm qilmanglar.
Bir–biringizga qarshi yovuz rejalar tuzmanglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Zakariyo 7:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-06'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 6 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='23' verse='25' id='Ex23v25'>
<text>Faqat Men, Egangiz Xudogagina,
xizmat qilinglar.
Shunda Men osh–suvingizni barakali qilaman,
orangizdan xastaliklarni yo‘q qilaman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 23:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='12' verse='26' id='J12v26'>
<text>Kim Menga xizmat qilmoqchi bo‘lsa, orqamdan yursin.
Men qayerda bo‘lsam, xizmatchim ham u yerda bo‘lsin.
Menga xizmat qilgan odamni Otam hurmat qiladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 12:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-07'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 7 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='40' id='J6v40'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>O‘g‘ilga ko‘z tikkan va Unga ishongan
har bir odam abadiy hayotga ega bo‘lishi
Otamning irodasidir.
Men bunday odamlarni oxiratda tiriltiraman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 6:40</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='16' id='J3v16'>
<text>Xudo olamni shunchalik sevdiki,
O‘zining yagona O‘g‘lini berdi.
Toki Unga ishonganlardan birontasi
halok bo‘lmasin,
balki abadiy hayotga ega bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 3:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-08'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 8 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='30' chapter='9' verse='15' id='Am9v15'>
<text>Men ularni o‘z yurtida ko‘kartiraman.
Men bergan yurtdan
Ularni hech kim sug‘urib tashlamaydi.
Egangizning kalomi shudir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Omo‘s 9:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='13' verse='28' id='Mc13v28'>
<text>Anjir daraxtidan saboq olinglar:
uning shoxlari ko‘karib barg chiqarayotganda,
yoz yaqinlashganini bilasizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 13:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-09'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 9 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='9' verse='15' id='Mt9v15'>
<text>Iso Yahyoning shogirdlariga dedi:
Kuyov davrada bo‘lganda to‘ydagi mehmonlar
qayg‘uradimi?
Biroq ular kuyovdan judo bo‘ladigan kunlar keladi,
ana o‘shanda ro‘za tutadilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 9:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='25' verse='1' id='Mt25v1'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Oxirzamon yaqinlashganda Osmon Shohligini
quyidagiga o‘xshatsa bo‘ladi:
kelinning o‘nta dugonasi moychiroqlarini olib,
kuyovni qarshilagani chiqishibdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 25:1</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-10'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 10 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='11' verse='7' id='Gn11v7'>
<intro>Egamiz dedi:</intro>
<text>Qani, pastga tushaylik–da,
ularning tilini aralashtirib yuboraylik,
toki birining gapini ikkinchisi tushunolmay qolsin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 11:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='17' verse='26' id='Act17v26'>
<text>Xudo bitta odamdan jamiki elatlarni yaratib,
ularni butun yer yuziga joylashtirdi.
U elatlarning hayoti vaqtini
va ular istiqomat qiladigan
joylarning chegaralarini belgilab berdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 17:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-11'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 11 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='35' verse='28' id='Ps35v28'>
<text>Odilliging haqidagi so‘zlaru madhing
Kun bo‘yi tilimdan tushmaydi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 34:28</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='51' verse='17' id='Ps51v17'>
<text>Lablarimni ochgin, ey Rabbiy,
Og‘zim Seni madh aylasin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 50:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-12'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 12 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='18' verse='4' id='Ez18v4'>
<text>Bilib qo‘ying,
har bir odamning joni Menikidir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 18:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='17' verse='6' id='J17v6'>
<intro>Iso Masih ibodat qildi:</intro>
<text>Sen dunyodan Menga bergan odamlarga
Seni tanitdim.
Ular Seniki edilar va Sen ularni Menga berding.
Ular Sening so‘zingga amal qildilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 17:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-13'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 13 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='27' verse='1' id='Ps27v1_D'>
<text><em>Dovud sanosi. </em>
Egam nurim va najotimdir,
Kimdan men qo‘rqardim?!
Egam hayotimning qal’asidir,
Kim meni qo‘rqita olar?!</text>
<ref>Zabur 26:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='56' chapter='2' verse='11' id='Tt2v11'>
<text>Qutqaruvchimiz Xudoning inoyati
butun odamlarga yaqqol oshkor bo‘ldi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Titus 2:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-14'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 14 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='37' verse='22' id='Gn37v22'>
<text>Ruben akalariga:
— qon to‘kmaylik —
dedi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 37:22</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='2' chapter='20' verse='13' id='Ex20v13'>
<text>Qotillik qilmang.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 20:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-15'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 15 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='7' verse='28' id='Mt7v28-29'>
<text>Iso bu gaplarini aytib bo‘lgandan keyin,
olomon Uning ta’limotidan hayratga tushdi.
Chunki Iso Tavrot tafsirchilariday emas,
balki hokimiyat egasiday ta’lim berar edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 7:28-29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='51' chapter='2' verse='3' id='Kol2v3'>
<text>Dnolik va ilmu ma’rifatning
hamma xazinalari Masihda pinhondir.</text>
<ref>Kolosaliklar 2:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-16'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 16 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='7' verse='3' id='Jr7v3'>
<text>Turmush tarzingizni o‘zgartiringlar.
Shundagina bu yurtda yashashingizga ijozat beraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 7:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='3' verse='16' id='1K3v16'>
<text>Nahotki bilmasangiz?
Sizlar Xudoning ma’badisizlar,
Xudoning Ruhi ichingizda yashamoqda.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 3:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-17'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 17 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='23' verse='28' id='Jr23v28'>
<text>Egamiz shunday demoqda:
Mayli, tush ko‘rgan payg‘ambar tushini aytsin,
so‘zimni eshitgan esa uni sadoqat bilan e’lon qilsin.
Axir, somon bilan bug‘doyning farqi bor–ku!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 23:28</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='2' verse='12' id='Mt2v12'>
<text>Munajjimlar tushlarida ogohlantirilgandan keyin,
boshqa yo‘l bilan o‘z yurtiga qaytib ketdilar.</text>
<ref>Matto 2:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-18'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 18 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='17' verse='16' id='1Rg17v16'>
<text>Egamizning Ilyos orqali aytganlariga binoan,
xumdagi un ham tamom bo‘lmadi,
xurmachadagi moy ham tugamadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 17:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='8' verse='18' id='Mc8v18-19'>
<intro>Iso shogirdlariga:</intro>
<text>Eslab ko‘ring: Men beshta nonni sindirib,
besh mingta erkakka bo‘lib berganimda,
sizlar qolgan non burdalari bilan nechta savatni
to‘ldirib olgansizlar?
— O‘n ikkita savatni, — deb javob berdi ular.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 8:18-19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-19'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 19 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='30' chapter='4' verse='11' id='Am4v11'>
<text>Sado‘m va G‘amo‘rani yo‘q qilganim kabi,
Men ko‘plaringizni yo‘q qildim.
Sizlar alangadan chiqarib olingan
yonayotgan o‘tinday edingizlar.
Shunda ham Menga qaytmadingizlar,
— deb aytmoqda Egamiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Omo‘s 4:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='2' verse='40' id='Act2v40'>
<text>Butrus boshqa ko‘p dalillar bilan
xaloyiqqa guvohlik berib:
O‘zlaringizni bu buzuq nasl ustiga kelayotgan
jazodan saqlanglar, deya o‘tindi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 2:40</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-20'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 20 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='35' verse='3' id='Is35v3'>
<text>Qo‘llari charchaganlarga dalda bergin,
Tizzalari bukilganlarga madad bergin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 35:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='12' verse='12' id='H12v12-13'>
<text>Qo‘llaringiz toliqqan, tizzalaringiz bukilgan,
ammo mahkam turing. O‘zingiz uchun to‘g‘ri yo‘lni tanlab yuring.
Toki orangizdagi “ojiz” va “oqsoq” odamlar yiqilmasin,
balki shifo topsinlar.</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 12:12-13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-21'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 21 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='3' verse='6' id='Gn3v6'>
<text>Xotin qarasaki, o‘sha daraxt ko‘zga chiroyli ko‘rinadi,
mevalari juda yeyishli ekan. Xotin:
“Qani, endi mevalar menga donolik ato qilsaydi”,
deb orzu qildi.
U daraxtning mevasidan olib yedi,
keyin yonida turgan eriga ham berdi. Eri ham yedi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 3:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='11' verse='34' id='L11v34'>
<text>Tananing chirog‘i — ko‘z.
Agar ko‘zingiz pok bo‘lsa,
butun taningiz yop–yorug‘ bo‘ladi.
Agarda ko‘zingiz yomon bo‘lsa,
butun tanangiz zimziyo zulmat bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 11:34</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-22'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 22 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='14' verse='12' id='L14v12'>
<text>Iso O‘zini taklif qilgan xonadon sohibiga aytdi:
Tushki yo kechki ziyofat berganingizda,
do‘stlaringizni yoki aka–ukalaringizni,
qarindosh–urug‘laringizni yo bo‘lmasa,
boy qo‘shnilaringizni taklif qilmang.
Aks holda, ular ham sizni mehmonga chaqirib,
qilgan yaxshiligingizni qaytaradilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 14:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='19' verse='17' id='Prv19v17'>
<text>Kambag‘alga rahm qilish —
Egamizga qarz berishday,
U yaxshilikni qaytaradi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 19:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-23'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 23 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='3' verse='30' id='R3v30'>
<text>Axir, Xudo yagona–ku!
Sunnatlilarni ham, sunnatsizlarni ham
Xudo imon orqali oqlaydi.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 3:30</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='11' verse='51' id='J11v51-52'>
<text>Iso nafaqat yahudiy xalqi uchun,
balki Xudoning tarqoq bo‘lgan hamma odamlarini
birlashtirish uchun o‘lishi kerak edi.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 11:51-52</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-24'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 24 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='39' verse='8' id='Ps39v8'>
<text>Kimdan men umid qilay endi, ey Rabbiy?
Sendadir mening barcha umidim.</text>
<ref>Zabur 38:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='5' verse='5' id='R5v5'>
<text>Umidimiz bizni uyatga qoldirmaydi.
Chunki bizga berilgan Muqaddas Ruh orqali
yuraklarimiz Xudoning mehr–muhabbati bilan to‘lib-toshadi.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 5:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-25'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 25 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='72' verse='10' id='Ps72v10'>
<text>Dengiz ortidagi yurtlarning shohlari,
Tarshish shohlari unga o‘lpon olib kelsinlar.
Shava hamda Savo shohlari
Unga hadyalar keltirsinlar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 71:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='2' verse='11' id='Mt2v11'>
<text>Munajjimlar uyga kirib,
chaqaloqni va Uning onasi Maryamni ko‘rdilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 2:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-26'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 26 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='16' verse='15' id='Mc16v15'>
<text>Iso shogirdlariga dedi:
Butun jahon bo‘ylab yuringlar va hamma
tirik jonga Xushxabarni e’lon qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 16:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='18' verse='8' id='Act18v8'>
<text>Sinagoganing qavmboshisi Krisp butun xonadoni
bilan Rabbimiz Isoga imon keltirdi.
Pavlusdan Xushxabar eshitgan Korinfliklarning
ko‘pchiligi ishonib, suvga cho‘mdirildilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 18:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-27'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 27 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='51' chapter='3' verse='8' id='Kol3v8-9'>
<text>Endi esa jahl, g‘azab, yovuzliklarning hammasini
bir chetga yig‘ishtirib qo‘yinglar.
Og‘zingizdan hech qanday jerkish yoki nojo‘ya
so‘z chiqmasin.
Bir-biringizga yolg‘on gapirmanglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 3:8-9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='2' verse='3' id='R2v3'>
<text>Ayni ishlarni o‘zing qila turib,
shunday ishlarni qiluvchilarni hukm etsang,
Xudoning hukmidan qochib qutulaman, deb o‘ylaysanmi? !</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 2:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-28'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 28 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='3' verse='19' id='Gn3v19'>
<text>Sen tuproqdan yaralgansan,
To tuproqqa qaytguningga qadar,
Peshana tering bilan non yeysan.
Zero, sen tuproqdirsan
Va tuproqqa qaytasan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 3:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='146' verse='4' id='Ps146v4'>
<text>Ular jon bergach, tuproqqa qaytar,
O‘sha ondayoq ularning rejasi yo‘qqa chiqar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 145:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-29'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 29 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='50' chapter='1' verse='27' id='Ph1v27'>
<text>Nima bo‘lishidan qat’iy nazar,
Masih Xushxabariga loyiq tarzda hayot
kechirishingiz kerak.</text>
<ref>Injil, Filipiliklar 1:27</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='1' chapter='6' verse='9' id='Gn6v9'>
<text>O‘sha davrda yer yuzidagi solih,
benuqson odam faqat Nuh bo‘lib,
Xudoga hamroh bo‘lib yashardi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 6:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-30'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 30 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='4' verse='22' id='L4v22'>
<text>Hamma Isoni maqtar edi.
Uning latif so‘zlariga mahliyo bo‘lib:
“Nahot bu Yusufning o‘g‘li bo‘lsa?!”
— deb aytishardi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 4:22</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='12' verse='49' id='J12v49'>
<intro>Iso Masih chaqirib dedi:</intro>
<text>Zotan Men O‘zimcha gapirganim yo‘q.
Meni yuborgan Ota nima aytishimni,
qanday gapirishimni Menga amr etgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 12:49</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-01-31'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 31 Yanvar 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='1' verse='17' id='Mt1v17'>
<text>Ibrohimdan Dovudgacha hammasi bo‘lib o‘n to‘rt nasl,
Dovuddan Bobildagi surgungacha o‘n to‘rt nasl
va Bobildagi surgundan Masih tug‘ilgungacha
o‘n to‘rt nasldir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 1:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='2' verse='4' id='L2v4-5'>
<text>Yusuf Jaliladagi Nosira shahridan
Yahudiyaning Baytlahm shahriga yo‘l oldi.
Bu shahar Dovud shahri edi.
Yusuf Dovud xonadonidan, uning naslidan edi.
Yusuf ro‘yxatdan o‘tgani Maryamni ham o‘zi bilan olib ketdi.
Maryam Yusufga unashtirilgan bo‘lib, farzand kutayotgan edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 2:4-5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-01'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 1 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='14' chapter='15' verse='2' id='2Chr15v2'>
<text>Sizlar Egamiz bilan bo‘lar ekansiz,
U ham sizlar bilan birga bo‘ladi.
Agar sizlar Egamizni izlasangizlar,
Uni topasizlar.
Agar Uni tark etsangizlar,
U ham sizlarni tark etadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Solnomalar 15:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='1' verse='13' id='2T1v13'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel Timofeyga yozgan:</intro>
<text>Sen mendan eshitgan sog‘lom ta’limotdan namuna olib,
Iso Masihning sadoqati va muhabbati bilan yo‘l tutgin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 1:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-02'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 2 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='31' id='Mt6v31-32'>
<text>Nima yeymiz, nima ichamiz, nima kiyamiz,
deb tashvishlanib yurmanglar.
Butparastlar hadeb bu narsalarning
tashvishida yuradilar.
Lekin osmondagi Otangiz bularning hammasiga
muhtoj ekaningizni biladi–ku!</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:31-32</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='17' verse='27' id='Act17v27'>
<text>Xudo har birimizdan uzoqda emas.</text>
<ref>Havoriylar 17:27</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-03'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 3 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='15' verse='5' id='R15v5-6'>
<text>Sabr va tasalli manbayi bo‘lgan Xudoning O‘zi
Iso Masihning shogirdlariga mos ravishda
bir–biringiz bilan hamfikr bo‘lishni
sizlarga ato qilsin.
Shunda sizlar yakdillik bilan,
bir ovozda Rabbimiz Iso Masihning Otasi —
Xudoni ulug‘laysizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 15:5-6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='50' chapter='2' verse='2' id='Ph2v2'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel yozgan:</intro>
<text>Mening shodligimga shodlik qo‘shib,
bir xil fikr qiling,
bir–biringizga mehr–muhabbat ko‘rsating,
yakdillik bilan hamfikr bo‘ling.</text>
<ref>Filipiliklar 2:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-04'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 4 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='49' chapter='4' verse='29' id='E4v29'>
<text>Og‘zingizdan hech qanday yaramas so‘z chiqmasin.
Lekin tinglovchilarning ehtiyojiga ko‘ra
kerakli gaplarni aytib, ularga dalda bering,
shunda so‘zlaringiz ularga foyda keltiradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 4:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='51' chapter='4' verse='6' id='Kol4v6'>
<text>Odamlar bilan gaplashganingizda
so‘zingiz hamisha yoqimli va mazmunli bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 4:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-05'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 5 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='29' chapter='4' verse='14' id='Joel4v14'>
<text>Ming–minglab olomon
To‘plangan Hukm vodiysida!
Zotan, yaqinlashgandir
Egamizning kuni Hukm vodiysiga.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yo‘il 3:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='4' verse='9' id='H4v9'>
<text>Xudoning xalqini Shabbat kuniga o‘xshagan farog‘at kutmoqda.</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 4:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-06'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 6 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='101' verse='2' id='Ps101v2'>
<intro>Dovud ibodati:</intro>
<text>Benuqson hayot kechirishni o‘rganaman,
Qachon bunga erishaman?
Pok yurak ila o‘z uyimda umr kechiraman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 100:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='52' chapter='4' verse='7' id='1Th4v7'>
<text>Xudo bizni harom yo‘ldan yurishga emas,
balki muqaddas bo‘lib yashashga chaqirdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 4:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-07'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 7 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='13' verse='6' id='Ps13v6'>
<text>Men umid bog‘layman sodiq sevgingga,
Najotingdan qalbim to‘ladi quvonchga.</text>
<ref>Zabur 12:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='77' verse='15' id='Ps77v15'>
<text>Mo‘jizalar yaratuvchi Xudo Sensan,
Xalqlar orasida qudratingni ko‘rsatgan Sensan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 76:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-08'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 8 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='31' verse='25' id='Ps31v25'>
<text>Bardam bo‘ling, dadil bo‘lsin yuragingiz,
Ey siz, Egamizdan umid qilganlar!</text>
<ref>Zabur 30:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='73' verse='26' id='Ps73v26'>
<text>Tugab borishi mumkin tanamu qalbim,
Ammo Sen, ey Xudo, qalbimning quvvatisan,
Sen to abad barqarorligimsan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 72:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-09'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 9 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='13' verse='19' id='L13v19'>
<text>Xudoning Shohligi bir odam o‘z bog‘iga ekkan xantal urug‘iga o‘xshaydi.
Urug‘ unib–o‘sib, daraxt bo‘ladi, qushlar uning shoxlariga uya quradi.</text>
<ref>Luqo 13:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='13' verse='29' id='L13v29'>
<text>Shundan keyin sharqu g‘arbdan,
shimolu janubdan odamlar kelib,
Xudoning Shohligida ziyofatga o‘tiradilar.</text>
<ref>Luqo 13:29</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-10'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 10 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='16' verse='14' id='Mc16v14'>
<text>Iso O‘zining yeb–ichib o‘tirgan o‘n bir shogirdiga
zohir bo‘ldi. Iso shogirdlarini imonlari zaifligi
va qaysarligi uchun koyidi, chunki ular Isoni tirilgan
holda ko‘rgan odamlarga ishonmagan edilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 16:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='3' verse='19' id='Ap3v19'>
<text>Men kimni sevsam, aybini ko‘rsataman,
tarbiyalayman.
Shunday ekan, shijoatli bo‘l,
gunohlaring uchun tavba qil.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 3:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-11'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 11 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='20' verse='15' id='Ex20v15'>
<text>O‘g‘irlik qilmang.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 20:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='6' chapter='7' verse='11' id='Jos7v11'>
<text>Isroil xalqi gunoh qildi,
ular bilan qilgan ahdimni buzdi.
Ular Menga bag‘ishlangan narsalardan
o‘g‘irlab olishdi.
Buning ustiga, aldab,
o‘g‘irlangan narsalarni o‘zlarining
narsalari orasiga yashirib qo‘ydilar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yoshua 7:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-12'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 12 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='20' chapter='24' verse='11' id='Prv24v11-12'>
<text>O‘limga mahkum bo‘lganlarni,
dorga olib ketilayotganlarni qutqar.
“Bilmayman”, — desang ham,
yurakni sinaydigan Xudo ko‘rmaydimi?</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 24:11-12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='10' chapter='15' verse='26' id='2Sm15v26'>
<text>Egam: “Sendan rozi emasman”, desa,
mayli, Unga nima ma’qul bo‘lsa, shuni qilsin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Shohlar 15:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-13'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 13 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='55' verse='12' id='Is55v12'>
<text>Ha, siz xursand bo‘lib borasiz,
Sog‘–omon qaytib kelasiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 55:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='10' verse='36' id='Act10v36'>
<text>U Isroil xalqiga yuborgan xabarni bilasizlar.
Tinchlik keltiradigan bu Xushxabarni Xudo
Iso Masih orqali e’lon qildi.
Iso Masih hammaning Rabbiysidir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 10:36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-14'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 14 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='49' chapter='6' verse='1' id='E6v1'>
<text>Ey farzandlar,
Rabbimiz Isoga tegishli bo‘lganingiz uchun
ota–onangizga itoat qilinglar,
chunki shunday qilish to‘g‘ridir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 6:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='6' verse='20' id='Prv6v20'>
<text>O‘g‘lim, otang nasihatlariga quloq sol,
onang o‘gitlarini rad etma.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 6:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-15'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 15 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='139' verse='14' id='Ps139v14'>
<text>Senga shukrona aytaman.
Axir, qanday ajoyib qilib yaratilganman!
Sening barcha ishlaring naqadar ajoyib,
Buni men juda yaxshi bilaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 138:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='44' verse='24' id='Is44v24'>
<text>Qutqaruvchingiz, onangiz qornida
sizga shakl bergan
Egamiz shunday aytmoqda:
Hammasini yaratgan Men Egangizman,
Yolg‘iz O‘zim samolarni yoyganman!
Bir O‘zim zaminni yaratganman!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 44:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-16'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 16 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='3' verse='13' id='Act3v13'>
<text>Bu odamga ota–bobolarimiz Ibrohim,
Is’hoq va Yoqubning Xudosi shifo berdi.
Shu orqali Xudo O‘zining quli Isoni ulug‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 3:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='3' verse='16' id='Mt3v16-17'>
<text>Iso suvga cho‘mdirildi. U suvdan chiqqan zahoti,
osmon ochilib ketdi va Iso O‘z ustiga
Xudoning Ruhi kaptar shaklida tushib qo‘nganini ko‘rdi.
Shu payt osmondan: “Bu Mening sevikli O‘g‘limdir,
Undan nihoyatda mamnunman”, — degan ovoz keldi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 3:16-17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-17'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 17 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='33' verse='20' id='Ex33v20'>
<intro>Rabbimiz Muso payg‘ambarga dedi:</intro>
<text>Lekin Mening yuzimni ko‘ra olmaysan.
Meni ko‘rgan odam tirik qolmaydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 33:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='36' chapter='1' verse='7' id='Zph1v7'>
<text>Egamiz Rabbiy oldida sukut saqlang!
Zero, Egamizning keladigan kuni
yaqinlashib qoldi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Safoniyo 1:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-18'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 18 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='118' verse='21' id='Ps118v21'>
<text>Ey Egam, ibodatimga javob berganing uchun,
Mening najotkorim bo‘lganing uchun
Senga shukrona aytaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 117:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='14' verse='30' id='Mt14v30'>
<text>Butrus shamolning kuchli ekanligidan
qo‘rqib ketdi. U suvga cho‘ka boshlab:
— Hazrat, meni qutqaring! — deb baqirdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 14:30</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-19'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 19 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='52' chapter='4' verse='3' id='1Th4v3'>
<text>Sizlarning muqaddas bo‘lishingiz
Xudoning irodasidir.
Shuning uchun jinsiy axloqsizlik qilmang.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 4:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='1' verse='1' id='Ps1v1-2'>
<text>Shunday insonlar saodatlidir:
Ular fosiqlar maslahatiga yurmaydi,
Gunohkorlar yo‘lida ular turmaydi,
Mazaxchilar orasida ular o‘tirmaydi.
Ha, ular Egamizning qonunidan zavq oladi,
Tunu kun ta’limotining mag‘zini chaqadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 1:1-2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-20'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 20 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='28' verse='16' id='Is28v16'>
<text>Egamiz Rabbiy aytmoqda:
Mana, Men joylashtiryapman Quddusda
Sinalgan bir toshni, poydevor toshini.
Bu qadrli tamal toshi, ishonchli poydevordir.
Ha, unga tayanganlar hech qachon umidsiz bo‘lmaydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 28:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='4' verse='22' id='J4v22'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Sizlar — Samariyaliklar kimga sajda
qilayotganingizni bilmaysizlar, bizlar esa
kimga sajda qilayotganimizni bilamiz.
Chunki najot yahudiylardan keladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 4:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-21'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 21 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='6' verse='13' id='Jr6v13-14'>
<text>Ular kichkinasidan tortib kattasigacha,
Nafsini tiyolmay harom yo‘l bilan pul topishadi.
Payg‘ambardan tortib ruhoniygacha —
Hammasi tovlamachilik qilishadi.
Xalqimning yaralarini yuzaki davolashadi.
Ahvol og‘ir bir paytda “hammasi yaxshi”,
deb aytishadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 6:13-14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='5' verse='2' id='1P5v2'>
<text>Xudoning nazoratingizdagi suruvini
yaxshi boqinglar.
Bu xizmatni majbur bo‘lganingiz uchun emas,
balki chin ko‘ngildan,
Xudoga manzur tarzda bajaringlar.
Shunchaki pulparastlik maqsadida emas,
samimiyat bilan ijro etinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Butrus 5:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-22'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 22 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='13' verse='3' id='J13v3'>
<text>Iso Otasi hamma narsani
Uning qo‘liga berganini bilar edi,
U Xudodan kelib, yana Xudoning oldiga
qaytayotganini ham bilar edi.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 13:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='26' verse='42' id='Mt26v42'>
<text>Iso ikkinchi marta ketib,
shunday deb iltijo qildi: Ey Otam!
Agar bu azob kosasidan qutulishimning iloji bo‘lmasa,
mayli, Men o‘sha kosadan ichaman.
Sening xohishing bajo bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 26:42</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-23'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 23 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='9' verse='3' id='Act9v3-5'>
<text>Shoul Damashqqa yaqinlashib qolganda,
birdan osmondan bir nur uning yon–atrofini yoritib yubordi.
Shoul yerga yiqilib, shunday bir ovozni eshitdi:
— Shoul, Shoul! Nega meni quvg‘in qilyapsan?
— Yo Hazratim! Sen kimsan? — deb so‘radi Shoul.
— Sen quvg‘in qilayotgan Isoman, — degan javob keldi.</text>
<ref>Havoriylar 9:3-5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='4' verse='6' id='2K4v6'>
<text>Xudo ibtidoda:
“Qorong‘ulikdan nur porlasin”, –
deb qanday buyurgan bo‘lsa,
endi O‘zining nuri bilan bizning
yuraklarimizni ham shunday yoritdi,
Iso Masih siymosida porlab turgan
O‘zining ulug‘vorligini bizga ko‘rsatdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 4:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-24'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 24 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='14' verse='13' id='Mt14v13-14'>
<text>Iso qayiqqa tushib, yolg‘iz O‘zi kimsasiz joyga suzib ketdi.
Olomon esa bu haqda eshitib, shaharlardan piyoda Uning
orqasidan ergashishdi. Iso qayiqdan chiqqanda,
katta bir olomonni ko‘rdi. Ularga achinib ketib,
xastalariga shifo berdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 14:13-14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='103' verse='13' id='Ps103v13'>
<text>Ota bolalariga shafqat qilganday,
Egamiz O‘zidan qo‘rqqanlarga rahm qiladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 102:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-25'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 25 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='77' verse='14' id='Ps77v14-15'>
<text>Sening yo‘ling, ey Xudo, muqaddasdir,
Qaysi Xudo Senday buyukdir?!
Mo‘jizalar yaratuvchi Xudo Sensan,
Xalqlar orasida qudratingni ko‘rsatgansan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 76:14-15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='68' id='J6v68-69'>
<text>Shimo‘n Butrus shunday javob berdi:
— Hazrat, biz Sizdan boshqa kimga ham borar edik? !
Abadiy hayot baxsh etuvchi so‘zlar Sizda–ku!
Biz ishonib bilamizki, Siz Xudoning Azizisiz.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 6:68-69</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-26'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 26 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='66' chapter='3' verse='4' id='Ap3v4'>
<text>Sardisda o‘z kiyimlarini bulg‘atmagan bir necha odamlaring qolgan.
Ular Men bilan birga oq kiyimda yuradilar, ular bunga loyiqdirlar.</text>
<ref>Vahiy 3:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='8' id='Mt5v8'>
<text>Pokdil bo‘lganlar baxtlidir,
Chunki ular Xudoni ko‘radilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-27'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 27 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='20' chapter='3' verse='29' id='Prv3v29'>
<text>Senga ishonib, yoningda tinchgina yashayotgan
qo‘shningga qarshi yomon niyat qilma.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 3:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='13' verse='8' id='R13v8'>
<text>Hech kimdan hech narsa qarzdor bo‘lmanglar.
Faqat mehr–muhabbatni ham farz, ham qarz deb bilinglar,
chunki o‘zgani yaxshi ko‘rgan odam Xudoning qonunini bajargan bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 13:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-02-28'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 28 Fevral 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='115' verse='16' id='Ps115v16'>
<text>Samolar Egamizning samolaridir,
Yerni esa U insonlarga bergandir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 113:24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='21' verse='33' id='Mt21v33'>
<text>Endi boshqa bir masalni eshitinglar:
bir yer egasi bor ekan. U uzumzor barpo qilibdi.
Atrof–tevaragini devor bilan o‘rab,
uzum siqadigan chuqur qazibdi,
kuzatuv minorasini quribdi.
Keyin uzumzorni bog‘bonlarga ijaraga berib,
o‘zi safarga ketibdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 21:33</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-01'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 1 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='97' id='Ps119v97'>
<text>O, naqadar sevaman qonuningni!
Kun bo‘yi xayolimda tutaman uni.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:97</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='18' id='Mt5v18'>
<text>Yeru osmon yo‘q bo‘lib ketishi mumkin.
Ammo Tavrotdagi na bir harf, na bir nuqta o‘chadi.
Unda yozilgan hamma narsa amalga oshadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-02'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 2 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='22' chapter='8' verse='6' id='Ct8v6-7'>
<text>Sevgi o‘limday kuchli,
Ishq ajalday shiddatlidir.
Sevgining uchqunlari olov uchqunlariday,
Lovullagan alangadaydir.
Suv sevgini o‘chirolmaydi,
To‘fonlar uni cho‘ktirolmaydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Sulaymonning go‘zal qo‘shig‘i 8:6-7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='15' verse='13' id='J15v13'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>Kim o‘z jonini do‘stlari uchun fido qilsa,
bundan ortiq sevgi yo‘q.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 15:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-03'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 3 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='14' verse='23' id='Mt14v23'>
<text>Iso odamlarni ketqizib yuborgandan keyin,
ibodat qilish uchun bir O‘zi tepalikka chiqdi.
Oqshom tushdi, U hamon o‘sha yerda yolg‘iz edi.</text>
<ref>Matto 14:23</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='13' verse='4' id='2K13v4'>
<text>Garchi Masih zaiflik holatida xochga mixlangan bo‘lsa-da,
Xudoning qudrati tufayli tirikdir.</text>
<ref>2 Korinfliklar 13:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-04'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 4 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='20' chapter='16' verse='6' id='Prv16v6'>
<text>Abadiy sevgi tufayli gunoh kechiriladi,
Egamizdan qo‘rqish yomonlikdan uzoqlashtiradi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 16:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='3' verse='15' id='1K3v15'>
<text>Kimning ishi yonsa, u talafot ko‘radi;
o‘zi qutuladi-yu,
ammo olovdan qutulib chiqqandek bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 3:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-05'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 5 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='5' verse='25' id='Act5v25'>
<text>Bir odam kelib, shunday xabar berdi:
— Sizlar qamoqqa tashlagan odamlar Ma’bad hovlisida turibdilar,
odamlarga ta’lim beryaptilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 5:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='8' verse='36' id='J8v36'>
<text>Agar O‘g‘il sizlarni ozod qilsa,
haqiqatan ozod bo‘lasizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 8:36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-06'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 6 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='80' verse='19' id='Ps80v19'>
<text>Senga sajda qilamiz,
bizga hayot ato qil.</text>
<ref>Zabur 79:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='138' verse='3' id='Ps138v3'>
<text>Chaqirganimda, menga javob bergansan,
Qudrating bilan meni jasur qilgansan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 137:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-07'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 7 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='4' chapter='20' verse='11' id='Nu20v11'>
<text>Muso qo‘lini ko‘tarib,
qoyaga tayog‘i bilan ikki marta urgan edi,
qoyadan sharillab suv oqdi. Jamoaning o‘zi ham,
ularning mollari ham suv ichdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Cho‘lda 20:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='10' verse='4' id='1K10v4'>
<text>Hammasi baravar ruhiy ichimlikni ichdilar;
ular orqalaridan kelayotgan ruhiy qoyatoshdan suv ichdilar.
U qoyatosh esa Masih edi.</text>
<ref>1 Korinfliklar 10:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-08'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 8 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='9' chapter='7' verse='3' id='1Sm7v3'>
<text>Shomuil jamiki Isroil xalqiga dedi:
— Agar chin dildan Egamizga qaytmoqchi bo‘lsangiz,
hamma begona xudolarni va Ashtaret
tasvirlarini orangizdan yo‘qoting.
Ko‘nglingizni Egamizga berib,
yolg‘iz Unga xizmat qiling.
Ana shunda Egamiz sizlarni Filistlarning
qo‘lidan qutqaradi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 7:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='8' verse='5' id='1K8v5-6'>
<text>Garchi yeru ko‘kda xudo deb atalgan mavjudotlar
bor bo‘lsa-da
(haqiqatan ham ko‘p “xudolar” va “rablar” bor),
lekin biz uchun birgina Otamiz Xudo bor.
Hamma narsa Undandir, biz U uchun yashaymiz.
Shuningdek, birgina Rabbimiz Iso Masih bor.
Hamma narsa U orqali vujudga kelgan,
biz ham U orqali yashaymiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 8:5-6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-09'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 9 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='89' verse='9' id='Ps89v9'>
<text>Ey Parvardigori Olam — Egam,
Kim senchalik qudratli, ey Egam? !
Sadoqating atrofingni o‘ragan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 88:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='8' verse='31' id='Mt8v31'>
<text>Jinlar Isoga yolvorib:
— Agar bizlarni quvib chiqaradigan bo‘lsang,
unda cho‘chqa podasiga yuborgin, — deyishdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 8:31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-10'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 10 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='118' verse='6' id='Ps118v6'>
<text>Egam men bilan birga, shu bois qo‘rqmayman.
Insonlar menga nima qila oladi?!</text>
<ref>Zabur 117:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='40' verse='5' id='Ps40v5'>
<text>Baxtlidir Egamizga umid bog‘laganlar,
Kiborlarga suyanmaganlar,
Butparastlardan yordam kutmaganlar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 39:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-11'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 11 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='45' id='Ps119v45'>
<text>Men ozod bo‘lib yuraveraman,
Buyruqlaringni izlab topganman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:45</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='3' verse='17' id='2K3v17'>
<text>Rabbimiz – Ruhdir.
Rabbimizning Ruhi qayerda bo‘lsa,
o‘sha yerda erkinlik bor.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 3:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-12'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 12 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='48' chapter='3' verse='26' id='G3v26'>
<text>Endi sizlar Iso Masihga bo‘lgan imoningiz
orqali Xudoning farzandisizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Galatiyaliklar 3:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='3' verse='1' id='1J3v1'>
<text>Qaranglar,
Otamiz Xudo bizni farzandlarim deb,
qanday buyuk bir sevgini ko‘rsatdi!</text>
<ref>1 Yuhanno 3:1</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-13'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 13 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='41' verse='55' id='Gn41v55'>
<text>Oxiri, Misr yurtida ham ocharchilik boshlandi.
Misr xalqi non so‘rab fir’avnga yolvordi.
Fir’avn esa xalqqa:
“Yusufga boringlar, u nima desa,
shuni qilinglar”, dedi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 41:55</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='13' id='J6v13'>
<text>Shogirdlar yeyilgan beshta arpa
nondan ortib qolgan burdalarni yig‘ib olishdi,
o‘n ikki savat to‘ldi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 6:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-14'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 14 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='26' verse='75' id='Mt26v75'>
<text>Butrus Isoning: “Xo‘roz qichqirmasidan oldin,
sen Mendan uch marta tonasan”,
degan gapini esladi.
U hovlidan chiqib, achchiq–achchiq yig‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 26:75</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='16' verse='24' id='Mt16v24'>
<text>Iso O‘z shogirdlariga dedi:
— Kimda–kim Menga ergashishni istasa,
o‘zidan kechsin va xochini ko‘tarib, orqamdan yursin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 16:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-15'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 15 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='78' verse='4' id='Ps78v4'>
<text>Egamizning hamdga loyiq ishlarini,
Uning qudratini, U qilgan ajoyibotlarni
Biz yashirmaymiz ularning bolalaridan,
Hikoya qilarmiz kelgusi avlodlarga ham.</text>
<ref>Zabur 77:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='34' verse='2' id='Ps34v2'>
<text>Har doim Egamni olqishlayman,
Uning madhi tilimdan aslo tushmaydi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 33:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-16'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 16 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='18' verse='23' id='Gn18v23-24'>
<intro>Ibrohim payg‘ambar Egasiga yalinib:</intro>
<text>Sen gunohkorni ham, begunohni ham birday
qirib tashlayverasanmi? Aytaylik,
shaharda ellikta begunoh odam topsang,
shaharni vayron qilaverasanmi?</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 18:23-24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='19' verse='41' id='L19v41-42'>
<text>Iso Quddusga kiray deganda,
shaharni ko‘rib, yig‘lab yubordi:
Tinchlik uchun nimalar zarurligini
bugun sen bilsayding!
Ammo bular senga qorong‘i.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 19:41-42</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-17'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 17 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='40' verse='13' id='Is40v13'>
<text>Kim Egamizning Ruhiga yo‘l ko‘rsatadi?!
Kim Unga maslahat beradi?!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 40:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='15' verse='26' id='J15v26'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men sizlarga Otamdan yuboradigan Homiy,
ya’ni Otamdan chiqqan Haqiqat Ruhi kelganda
Men to‘g‘rimda guvohlik beradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 15:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-18'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 18 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='24' verse='7' id='L24v7'>
<text>Inson O‘g‘li gunohkor odamlar qo‘liga
tutib beriladi,
xochga mixlanadi, uchinchi kuni esa tiriladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 24:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='43' id='1K15v43'>
<text>Tushkunlikda ekiladi-yu, ulug‘vorlik bilan tiriladi;
zaiflikda ekiladi-yu, qudrat bilan tiriladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:43</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-19'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 19 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='9' verse='7' id='Mc9v7-8'>
<text>Shu paytda bulut paydo bo‘lib, ularga soya soldi.
Bulut orasidan shunday ovoz eshitildi:
— Bu Mening sevikli O‘g‘limdir, Unga quloq solinglar!
Birdaniga shogirdlar atrofga qarab,
yolg‘iz Isodan boshqa hech kimni ko‘rishmadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 9:7-8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='12' verse='45' id='J12v45'>
<intro>Iso Masih chaqirib dedi:</intro>
<text>Meni ko‘rgan odam Meni Yuborganni ko‘rgan bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 12:45</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-20'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 20 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='49' chapter='4' verse='3' id='E4v3'>
<text>O‘zaro tinch–totuv yashab,
Muqaddas Ruh ato qilgan birdamlikni
saqlashga jon kuydiringlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 4:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='12' verse='18' id='R12v18'>
<text>Agar iloji bo‘lsa, qo‘lingizdan kelganicha,
barcha odamlar bilan tinch-totuv hayot kechiringlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 12:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-21'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 21 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='23' verse='7' id='Ex23v7'>
<text>Tuhmatchilardan uzoq turinglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 23:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='4' verse='28' id='E4v28'>
<text>Oldin o‘g‘ri bo‘lgan endi o‘g‘rilik qilmasin,
balki ishlasin,
o‘z qo‘llari bilan mehnat qilsin–da,
topganini muhtoj bo‘lganlar bilan baham ko‘rsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 4:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-22'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 22 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='4' verse='36' id='J4v36'>
<text>O‘roqchi hozirdan yaxshi daromad olmoqda,
abadiy hayot uchun hosil yig‘moqda.
Toki hosilni ekkan va o‘rgan birga quvonishsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 4:36</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='3' verse='8' id='1K3v8'>
<text>Ekuvchi va sug‘oruvchining mohiyati bir,
har biri mukofotni o‘z mehnatiga yarasha oladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 3:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-23'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 23 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='28' chapter='11' verse='4' id='Hos11v4'>
<text>Egamiz shunday deydi:
Men Isroilni mehr ila yetaklagandim,
Muhabbat rishtalari ila olib yurgan edim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ho‘shiyo 11:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='16' verse='30' id='Act16v30-31'>
<text>Zindonbon ikkovini tashqariga olib chiqib:
“Janoblar, najot topishim uchun nima qilishim kerak?” deb so‘radi.
“Rabbimiz Isoga ishon,
shunda o‘zing va xonadon ahling
najot topasizlar,”
deb javob berishdi ular.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 16:30-31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-24'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 24 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='38' verse='22' id='Ps38v22'>
<text>Ey Egam, meni aslo tark etmagin,
Ey Xudoyim, mendan uzoq ketmagin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 37:22</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='33' verse='4' id='Ps33v4'>
<text>Egamizning kalomi haqiqatdir,
Uning barcha ishlari ishonchlidir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 32:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-25'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 25 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='65' verse='8' id='Is65v8'>
<text>Egamiz shunday aytmoqda:
Agar bir bosh uzumda hali sharbati bor bo‘lsa,
Odamlar: ‘Uni tashlab yubormang,
Hali foydasi tegadi’, deb aytadi.
Men ham O‘z qullarim haqi shunday qilaman,
O‘z xalqimning hammasini yo‘q qilmayman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 65:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='11' verse='5' id='R11v5'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel Isroil xalqi haqida</intro>
<text>Hozir ham Xudoga sodiq qolganlar bor,
chunki ular Xudoning inoyati bo‘yicha tanlanganlar.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 11:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-26'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 26 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='5' verse='33' id='Mc5v33-34'>
<text>Ayol o‘zida qanday o‘zgarish bo‘lganini bilib,
titrab–qo‘rqib keldi,
Isoning oyoqlari ostiga o‘zini tashlab,
butun haqiqatni Unga so‘zlab berdi.
Iso unga dedi:
— Qizim, ishonching seni sog‘aytirdi.
Eson–omon bor, dardingdan xalos bo‘lgin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 5:33-34</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='10' verse='52' id='Mc10v52'>
<text>Iso ko‘r Bartimeyga:
— Boraver, ishonching seni sog‘aytirdi, — dedi.
O‘sha zahoti u ko‘ra boshladi.
So‘ng Isoning ortidan ergashib ketdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 10:52</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-27'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 27 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='5' verse='19' id='Mc5v19'>
<text>Iso shifo topgan odamga:
Uyingga bor, — dedi —
Men — Rabbing sen uchun nimalar qilganimni,
qanday rahm–shafqat ko‘rsatganimni
o‘z yaqinlaringga gapirib ber.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 5:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='6' verse='12' id='Mc6v12-13'>
<text>Havoriylar yo‘l yurib,
tavba qilinglar, deb hammani da’vat qilishdi.
Ular ko‘p jinlarni quvib chiqarishdi
va ko‘p xastalarga moy surtib
ularni sog‘aytirishdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 6:12-13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-28'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 28 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='34' verse='5' id='Ps34v5'>
<text>Egamga yuz burdim, U javob berdi,
Hamma qo‘rquvlardan U xalos qildi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 33:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='50' verse='15' id='Ps50v15'>
<text>Og‘ir kunda Menga iltijo qilgin,
Senga najot beraman,
Sen esa Menga maqtov aytasan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 49:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-29'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 29 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='95' verse='6' id='Ps95v6'>
<text>Kelinglar, ta’zim qilib, sajda etaylik,
Yaratgan Egamiz oldida tiz cho‘kaylik.</text>
<ref>Zabur 94:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='21' verse='5' id='Act21v5'>
<text>Imonlilarning hammasi, xotinlari va
bola–chaqalari bilan birga bizni shahar
tashqarisigacha kuzatib chiqdi.
Dengiz bo‘yida tiz cho‘kib, ibodat qildik.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 21:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-30'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 30 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='9' verse='8' id='Gn9v8-10'>
<text>Xudo Nuh bilan uning o‘g‘illariga yana gapirdi:
Men endi sizlar bilan va sizlarning
avlodingiz bilan ahd qilaman.
Sizlar bilan kemadan chiqqan hamma tirik
jonzotlar bilan ham ahd qilaman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 9:8-10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='26' chapter='1' verse='28' id='Ez1v28'>
<text>O‘sha nur yomg‘irdan keyin bulutlar orasida
paydo bo‘ladigan kamalakdek jilvalanardi.
Bu yog‘du Egamizning ulug‘vorligini aks etardi.
Men buni ko‘rishim bilanoq yerga muk tushdim,
so‘ng bir ovoz eshitdim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 1:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-03-31'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 31 Mart 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='103' verse='11' id='Ps103v11'>
<text>Samolar zamindan naqadar balanddir!
Egamizning sodiq sevgisi ham
Undan qo‘rqqanlarga shunday yuksakdir!</text>
<ref>Zabur 102:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='7' verse='11' id='Mt7v11'>
<text>Sizlar gunohkor bo‘la turib
bolalaringizga yaxshi hadyalar bera olar ekansiz,
osmondagi Otangiz ham Undan so‘raganlarga
a’lo ne’matlar berishga qanchalar tayyor!</text>
<ref>Matto 7:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-01'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 1 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='48' chapter='1' verse='8' id='G1v8'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Kimda–kim, hatto biz o‘zimizmi
yoki osmondan kelgan biror farishtami,
sizlarga biz yetkazgan Xushxabardan boshqa bir
“xushxabar” keltirsa, la’nati bo‘lsin!</text>
<ref>Injil, Galatiyaliklar 1:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='54' chapter='4' verse='16' id='1T4v16'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus Timofeyga yozgan:</intro>
<text>O‘zingga va ta’limotingga ehtiyot bo‘l,
faoliyatingni astoydil davom ettir.
Bu bilan o‘zingni ham,
tinglovchilaringni ham qutqarasan.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Timo‘tiy 4:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-02'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 2 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='27' chapter='10' verse='11' id='Dn10v11'>
<text>Doniyorga farishta ko‘rinib:
— Ey, Doniyor, sen Xudoning suyukli bandasisan, — dedi.
— Qani, tur! Senga aytadigan gaplarimga quloq sol,
chunki men sening oldingga yuborilganman.
U bu gaplarini menga aytayotganda
men qaltirab o‘rnimdan turdim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Doniyor 10:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='2' chapter='24' verse='7' id='Ex24v7'>
<text>Egamizning hamma aytganlarini bajaramiz,
Unga itoat qilamiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 24:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-03'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 3 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='7' verse='9' id='Ps7v9'>
<text>Xalqlarni hukm qil Sen, ey Egam,
Ey Egam, mening ham yuzimni yorug‘ qil.</text>
<ref>Zabur 7:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='16' verse='7' id='Ap16v7'>
<text>Qurbongohdan bir ovoz eshitildi,
u shunday dedi:
“Ha, Qodir Xudo — Egamiz!
Sening hukmlaring haq va adolatlidir.”</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 16:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-04'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 4 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='1' verse='31' id='Mc1v31'>
<text>Iso ayolning yoniga bordi,
qo‘lidan tutib, o‘tirg‘izib qo‘ydi.
Shunda ayolning isitmasi tushdi,
u mehmonlarga xizmat qila boshladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 1:31</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='116' verse='12' id='Ps116v12'>
<text>Egamga nima bilan qaytaray
Menga qilgan barcha yaxshiliklari uchun?</text>
<ref>Zabur 115:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-05'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 5 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='47' chapter='2' verse='14' id='2K2v14'>
<text>Xudoga shukr! U bizni doimo Masihning
tantanali yurishida olib borayotir
va biz orqali har yerda O‘z haqidagi
bilimning xush bo‘ylarini tarqatayotir.</text>
<ref>2 Korinfliklar 2:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='16' id='Mt5v16'>
<text>Sizning nuringiz insonlar oldida shunday porlasinki,
toki ular yaxshi ishlaringizni ko‘rib,
osmondagi Otangizni ulug‘lasinlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-06'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 6 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='1' verse='1' id='Gn1v1'>
<text>Xudo azalda osmon bilan yerni yaratdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 1:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='136' verse='2' id='Ps136v2'>
<text>Shukrona ayting xudolarning Xudosiga,
Uning sodiq sevgisi abadiydir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 135:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-07'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 7 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='8' verse='29' id='Mc8v29'>
<text>Iso ulardan so‘radi:
— Sizlar–chi, Meni kim deb bilasiz?
Butrus Unga javob berib:
— Siz Masihsiz, — dedi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 8:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='27' verse='54' id='Mt27v54'>
<text>Isoni qo‘riqlab turgan yuzboshi bilan yonidagi askarlar zilzilani va
sodir bo‘layotgan barcha ishlarni ko‘rib, vahimaga tushdilar. Ular:
— Haqiqatan ham bu Odam Xudoning O‘g‘li ekan! — dedilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 27:54</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-08'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 8 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='91' verse='1' id='Ps91v1-2'>
<text>Xudoyi Taolo panohida yashaydiganlar
Qodir Xudo soyasida orom topar.
Men Egamga shunday deyman:
“Sen panohimsan, qal’amsan,
Men umid bog‘lagan Xudoyimsan.”</text>
<ref>Zabur 90:1-2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='8' verse='31' id='R8v31'>
<text>Xudo biz tomon bo‘lsa,
kim bizga qarshi chiqar ekan?!</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 8:31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-09'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 9 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='11' verse='14' id='Mt11v14'>
<intro>Iso Masih Yahyo payg‘ambar to‘g‘risida:</intro>
<text>Agar bu bashoratlarga ishonishni istasangizlar,
Yahyo — kelishi bashorat qilingan Ilyosdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 11:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='1' verse='17' id='L1v17'>
<text>Yahyo Ilyos payg‘ambarning ruhi va qudratiga to‘lib,
Rabbimiz Masihdan oldin keladi.
Rabbimizga tayyor bir xalqni taqdim qilish uchun,
otalarning yuraklarini farzandlariga moyil qiladi,
itoatsizlarning fikrini solihlar donoligi tomon buradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 1:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-10'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 10 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='6' verse='7' id='Mc6v7'>
<text>O‘n ikki havoriyni yoniga chaqirib,
ikkita–ikkitadan qilib jo‘nata boshladi.
Ularga yovuz ruhlar ustidan hokimiyat berdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 6:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='28' verse='18' id='Mt28v18-20'>
<text>Iso dedi:
“Yeru osmondagi butun hokimiyat Menga berilgan.
Shuning uchun borib, barcha xalqlardan shogird orttiringlar.
Ularni Ota, O‘g‘il va Muqaddas Ruh nomi bilan suvga cho‘mdiringlar.
Men sizlarga buyurgan hamma narsaga amal qilishni
ularga o‘rgatinglar.”</text>
<ref>Matto 28:18-20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-11'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 11 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='51' chapter='3' verse='12' id='Kol3v12'>
<text>Sizlar Xudoning tanlangan, aziz va suyukli xalqisizlar.
Shunga ko‘ra rahm-shafqat, mehribonlik, kamtarlik,
muloyimlik va sabr-toqatni zeb-ziynat qilib taqib olinglar.</text>
<ref>Kolosaliklar 3:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='39' id='Mt5v39'>
<text>Sizga yomonlik qilgan odamga qarshilik ko‘rsatmang.
Agar kimdir o‘ng chakkangizga ursa,
unga chapini ham tuting.</text>
<ref>Matto 5:39</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-12'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 12 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='62' verse='10' id='Ps62v10'>
<text>Inson zoti bir nafasdir,
Ha, inson zoti yolg‘ondir!
Agar tarozida tortib ko‘rilsa,
Hammasi birga havodan ham yengil chiqadi.
Ularning aslo vazni yo‘qdir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 61:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='42' id='1K15v42'>
<text>O‘liklarning tirilishi bunga o‘xshaydi:
tana o‘tkinchi bo‘lib ekiladi-yu, o‘lmaydigan bo‘lib tiriladi.</text>
<ref>1 Korinfliklar 15:42</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-13'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 13 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='8' verse='12' id='J8v12'>
<text>Iso xalqqa gapirib dedi:
— Men olamning nuriman.
Kimki Menga ergashsa,
hech qachon zulmatda yurmaydi,
balki hayot nuriga ega bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 8:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='4' verse='4' id='2K4v4'>
<text>Xudoning tasviri bo‘lgan Masihning ulug‘vor
Xushxabarining nurini odamlar ko‘rmasin deb,
bu dunyoning tangrisi (shayton) imonsizlarning
zehnlarini ko‘r qilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 4:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-14'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 14 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='19' verse='13' id='Gn19v13'>
<intro>Farishtalar Lutga:</intro>
<text>Biz shaharni butunlay qirib tashlaymiz.
Egamiz bu shahar xalqining jinoyatlari
g‘oyat dahshatli ekani to‘g‘risida eshitib,
bu shaharni qirib tashlanglar,
deb bizni yubordi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 19:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='33' verse='10' id='Ps33v10'>
<text>Egamiz xalqlarning rejalarini parokanda qiladi,
U xalqlarning niyatlarini puchga chiqaradi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 32:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-15'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 15 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='51' chapter='3' verse='25' id='Kol3v25'>
<text>Kimki nohaqlik qilsa,
qilmishiga yarasha jazo oladi.
Zero, Xudo tarafkashlik qilmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 3:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='1' verse='17' id='1P1v17'>
<text>Sizlar Xudoga iltijo qilib, Uni Ota deb ataysizlar.
Ammo esingizda tutinglar, Xudo yuz–xotirchilik qilmaydi,
U har bir kishini qilgan ishiga yarasha taqdirlaydi yoki jazolaydi.
Shunday ekan, bu dunyodagi musofirchilik davringizda
Xudodan qo‘rqib yashanglar.</text>
<ref>1 Butrus 1:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-16'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 16 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='10' verse='17' id='Ps10v17'>
<text>Ey Egam,
mazlumlarning istaklariga quloq solasan,
Ularning yuraklariga dalda berasan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 9:38</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='8' verse='25' id='Mt8v25-26'>
<text>Shogirdlari Isoning oldiga borib:
— Hazrat, bizni qutqaring! Halok bo‘lyapmiz!
— deb Isoni uyg‘otdilar. Iso ularga dedi:
— Nega qo‘rqyapsizlar, ey imoni sustlar?
So‘ng turib, shamolga va to‘lqinlarga do‘q urdi.
Shu ondayoq chuqur sukunat cho‘kdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 8:25-26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-17'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 17 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='58' chapter='10' verse='25' id='H10v25'>
<text>Ba’zi odamlarga o‘xshab, yig‘ilishlarimizni qoldirmaylik.
Aksincha, Rabbimiz Isoning keladigan kuni
yaqinlashib qolganini bilib,
bir–birimizga yanada ko‘proq dalda beraylik.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 10:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='81' verse='14' id='Ps81v14'>
<text>Eh, qaniydi siz Menga quloq solsangiz,
Ey Isroil, Mening yo‘llarimdan yursangiz!</text>
<ref>Zabur 80:14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-18'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 18 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='1' verse='5' id='J1v5'>
<text>Nur zulmatda porlaydi,
Zulmat esa Nurni yengolmadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 1:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='5' verse='8' id='E5v8-9'>
<text>Bir vaqtlar sizlar zulmatga to‘la edingiz,
endi esa Rabbimiz Isoga tegishli bo‘lganingiz uchun nurga to‘ldingiz.
Shunday ekan, nurga to‘la insonlar kabi yashanglar.
Axir, har qanday ezgulik, solihlik va haqiqat
nurning samarasidir.</text>
<ref>Efesliklar 5:8-9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-19'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 19 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='16' verse='8' id='Mt16v8-9'>
<text>Iso shogirdlariga dedi:
Ey imoni sustlar!
Nega sizlar, nonimiz yo‘q, deb aytyapsizlar?
Hali ham tushunmadingizlarmi?
Besh mingta odamga beshta nonni bo‘lib berganim
esingizdami? O‘shanda qolgan–qutgan nonlar bilan
qancha savatni to‘ldirib olgan edingizlar?</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 16,8-9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='26' chapter='36' verse='23' id='Ez36v23'>
<text>Sizlar bulg‘agan Mening buyuk nomim
qanchalik muqaddas ekanligini
Men barcha xalqlarga ko‘rsataman.
O‘shanda Egasi Men ekanligimni ular bilib oladilar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 36:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-20'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 20 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='2' verse='2' id='Jr2v2'>
<text>Egangiz shunday deb aytmoqda:
Yoshligingdagi vafodorliging yodimda,
Kelinchakligingdagi sevging esimda.
Sen sahroda Menga ergashgan eding,
Ekin ekilmagan yerda orqamdan yurar eding.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 2:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='6' verse='10' id='H6v10'>
<text>Xudo adolatlidir. U sizning ishingizni unutmaydi,
Unga bo‘lgan muhabbatingiz tufayli
azizlariga qilgan va qilayotgan xizmatlaringizni yodida tutadi.</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 6:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-21'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 21 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='19' verse='17' id='Mt19v17'>
<text>Iso yigitga dedi:
Nega Mendan yaxshi ish to‘g‘risida so‘rayapsiz?
Birgina Xudodan boshqa hech kim yaxshi emas.
Abadiy hayotdan bahramand bo‘lishni istasangiz,
Xudoning amrlariga rioya qiling.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 19:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='24' chapter='9' verse='22' id='Jr9v22-23'>
<text>Egamiz shunday deb aytmoqda:
Donolar donoligi bilan maqtanmasin.
Kuchlilar kuchi bilan maqtanmasin.
Boylar boyligi bilan maqtanmasin.
Kim maqtanmoqchi bo‘lsa,
Xudoni bilaman, deb maqtansin,
Xudoni tushunaman, deb maqtansin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 9:23-24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-22'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 22 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='3' verse='8' id='Gn3v8'>
<text>Odam va xotini Parvardigor Egamizning nazaridan qochib,
bog‘dagi daraxtlar orasiga yashirindilar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 3:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='100' verse='1' id='Ps100v1-2'>
<text>Ey zamin ahli,
Egamizga shodlik ila hayqiring,
Xursand bo‘lib Egamizga sajdalar qiling,
Shodlanib, qo‘shiq aytib, Uning huzuriga keling.</text>
<ref>Zabur 99:1-2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-23'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 23 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='25' chapter='3' verse='57' id='Thr3v57'>
<text>Yolvorganimda Sen menga yaqinlashding,
Qo‘rqma! deb o‘shanda menga aytding.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyoning marsiyasi 3:57</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='10' verse='12' id='R10v12-13'>
<text>Yahudiylar bilan g‘ayriyahudiylar orasida
aslo farq yo‘q.
Ularning Rabbiysi bir bo‘lib,
Unga iltijo qilganlarning birontasidan
O‘z mehr–shafqatini ayamaydi.
Axir,
“Rabbimizga iltijo qilgan har bir inson qutqariladi”,
deb yozilgan–ku.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 10:12-13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-24'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 24 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='145' verse='17' id='Ps145v17'>
<text>Egamiz hamma yo‘llarida adolat qilar,
Hamma ishlarida sevgisini ko‘rsatar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 144:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='11' verse='29' id='R11v29'>
<text>Xudo bergan in’omlarini qaytarib olmaydi
va O‘zi da’vat qilgan xalqidan voz kechmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 11:29</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-25'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 25 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='52' chapter='5' verse='8' id='1Th5v8'>
<text>Biz kunduz kunga tegishli ekanmiz,
kelinglar, imon va sevgini sovut qilib,
boshimizga esa najot umidini
dubulg‘a qilib kiyib,
hushyor bo‘laylik.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 5:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='1' verse='7' id='1J1v7'>
<text>Bordi–yu, Xudo singari nurda yashasak,
biz birodarlarimiz bilan uyg‘unlikda yashaymiz
va Xudo O‘z O‘g‘li Isoning qoni orqali
bizni har qanday gunohdan poklaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 1:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-26'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 26 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='4' verse='51' id='J4v51'>
<text>Saroy amaldori hamon yo‘lda ekan,
xizmatkorlari unga peshvoz chiqib:
— O‘g‘lingiz sog‘–salomat, — degan xabar keltirdilar.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 4:51</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='5' verse='25' id='J5v25'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>O‘liklar Xudo O‘g‘lining ovozini eshitadigan
vaqt keladi, kelib qoldi ham.
O‘g‘ilning ovoziga quloq solganlar
tiriladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 5:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-27'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 27 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='5' id='1K15v5'>
<text>Masih avval Kifaga,
so‘ngra o‘n ikki shogirdiga ko‘rindi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='1' verse='10' id='2T1v10'>
<text>Xudoning inoyati endi Xaloskorimiz Iso Masihning
olamga kelishi bilan ochiq namoyon bo‘ldi.
Injil Xushxabari shundan iboratki,
Iso Masih o‘limni yo‘qqa chiqardi,
hayot va o‘lmaslikni esa oydinlikka chiqardi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 1:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-28'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 28 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='60' verse='10' id='Is60v10'>
<text>Egamiz Quddusga shunday deydi:
Begonalar devorlaringni tuzatadi,
Shohlari senga xizmat qiladi.
G‘azablanganimda senga jazo bergan bo‘lsam ham,
Endi marhamat qilib, senga shafqat qilaman.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 60:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='33' chapter='7' verse='19' id='Mch7v19'>
<text>Sen bizga yana rahm qilasan.
Ayblarimizni ko‘mib yuborasan,
Gunohlarimizni dengiz tubiga uloqtirasan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Mixo 7:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-29'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 29 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='32' verse='42' id='Jr32v42'>
<text>Egamiz shunday demoqda:
Men bu xalqning boshiga katta falokatni
qanday yog‘dirgan bo‘lsam,
va’da qilgan barcha ezguliklarimni ham
ustilariga xuddi shunday yog‘diraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 32:42</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='4' verse='7' id='Ps4v7'>
<text>Ey Egam, odamlar shunday deb aytadi:
“Yaxshi zamonlarni kim bizga ko‘rsatadi?”
Ey Egam, jamoling bizga nurlarini sochsin!</text>
<ref>Zabur 4:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-04-30'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 30 Aprel 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='6' verse='8' id='Gn6v8'>
<text>Nuh Egamizning marhamatiga sazovor bo‘lgan edi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 6:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='13' verse='13' id='2K13v13'>
<text>Rabbimiz Iso Masihning inoyati,
Otamiz Xudoning sevgisi va
Muqaddas Ruhning hamrohligi
hammangizga yor bo‘lsin! Omin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 13:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-01'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 1 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='16' verse='8' id='Ps16v8'>
<text>Men doim Egamni birinchi o‘ringa qo‘yaman,
U o‘ng tomonimda bo‘lgani uchun
Meni hech narsa qo‘zg‘ata olmas.</text>
<ref>Zabur 15:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='21' verse='28' id='L21v28'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Bu hodisalar yuz bera boshlaganda,
turib, boshingizni baland ko‘taring.
Chunki qutqariladigan vaqtingiz yaqinlashmoqda.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 21:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-02'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 2 May 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='10' verse='21' id='L10v21'>
<text>Shu on Iso Muqaddas Ruhning shodligiga to‘lib, dedi:
Ey Ota, yeru osmonning Egasi!
Sen bu ishlarni donolaru idroklilardan yashirib,
go‘daklarga ma’lum etganing uchun Senga shukrlar aytaman.
Ha Ota, bu Sening ezgu xohishing edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 10:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='1' verse='20' id='1K1v20'>
<text>Dono qayerda? Olim qayerda?
Bu dunyoning notiqi qayerda?
Dunyoning hikmatini Xudo aqlsizlikka
aylantirgani yo‘qmi?!</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 1:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-03'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 3 May 2017</title>
<parol book='58' chapter='2' verse='3' id='H2v3'>
<text>Nahotki biz buyuk najot xabariga e’tiborsiz
qolsak jazodan qochib qutula olamiz?!
Axir, dastlab bu najot xabarini bizga
Rabbimiz Isoning O‘zi e’lon qildi–ku.
Rabbimizga quloq solgan shohidlar bu xabarning
haqiqiyligini bizga tasdiqlashdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 2:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='139' verse='9' id='Ps139v9-10'>
<text>Saharning qanotlarini olib parvoz qilsam,
Dengizning eng uzoq chetlariga o‘rnashsam,
Hatto u yerda ham qo‘llaring meni yetaklar,
O‘ng qo‘ling meni quvvatlar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 138:9-10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-04'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 4 May 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='37' verse='23' id='Ez37v23'>
<text>Ular gunoh qilib, yashagan hamma
manzilgohlardan Men ularni xalos qilaman.
Dillarini poklab tozalayman.
Shunda ular Mening xalqim,
Men esa ularning Xudosi bo‘laman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 37:23</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='21' verse='3' id='Ap21v3'>
<intro>Havoriy Yuhanno yozgan:</intro>
<text>Men taxtdan baland bir ovoz
kelganini eshitdim. O‘sha ovoz dedi:
Xudoning maskani insonlar orasidadir!
U endi odamlar orasida yashaydi,
Ular Xudoning xalqi bo‘ladilar.
Xudoning O‘zi ular bilan birga bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 21:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-05'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 5 May 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='26' verse='3' id='Gn26v3'>
<text>O‘sha yerda yashab tur.
Agar shunday qilsang,
Men sen bilan birga bo‘laman,
senga baraka beraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 26:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='9' verse='16' id='R9v16'>
<text>Xudoning mehr–shafqati
inson xohishi va tashabbusiga emas,
balki Xudoning irodasiga bog‘liq.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 9:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-06'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 6 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='33' verse='9' id='Ps33v9'>
<text>U gapirdi, aytgani mavjud bo‘ldi,
Amr qildi, zamin yaratildi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 32:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='21' verse='33' id='L21v33'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytmoqda:</intro>
<text>Yeru osmon yo‘q bo‘lib ketadi,
ammo Mening so‘zlarim kuchda qoladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 21:33</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-07'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 7 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='117' verse='1' id='Ps117v1'>
<text>Ey barcha xalqlar,
Egamizga hamdu sanolar bo‘lsin!
Ey jamiki elatlar, Uni olqishlanglar!</text>
<ref>Zabur 116:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='11' chapter='8' verse='60' id='1Rg8v60'>
<text>Dunyodagi jamiki qavmlar
Egamiz — Xudo ekanini bilib qo‘ysin.
Undan boshqasi yo‘q.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 8:60</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-08'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 8 May 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='4' verse='20' id='1K4v20'>
<text>Xudo saltanati so‘zda emas,
balki quvvatdadir.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 4:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='14' chapter='25' verse='8' id='2Chr25v8'>
<text>Sen jasorat bilan jang qilsang ham,
baribir Xudo seni g‘animlaring oldida mag‘lub qiladi,
chunki yordam beradigan va mag‘lub qiladigan Xudodir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Solnomalar 25:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-09'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 9 May 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='13' id='Mt5v13'>
<text>Sizlar yerning tuzisizlar.
Lekin tuz o‘z ta’mini yo‘qotsa,
uni yana qanday sho‘r qilib bo‘ladi?</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='3' verse='15' id='Ap3v15-16'>
<text>Sening ishlaringni bilaman,
sen na sovuq va na issiqsan.
Eh, qani edi yo sovuq, yo issiq bo‘lsang!
Sen issiq ham, sovuq ham emas,
balki iliq bo‘lganing uchun Men seni qusib yuboraman.</text>
<ref>Vahiy 3:15-16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-10'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 10 May 2017</title>
<parol book='10' chapter='7' verse='18' id='2Sm7v18'>
<text>Shoh Dovud Egamizning huzurida o‘tirib,
shunday ibodat qildi:
Ey, Egamiz Rabbiy! Men kim bo‘libman,
xonadonim nima bo‘libdiki,
Sen meni bu qadar ulug‘lading?!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Shohlar 7:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='10' id='1K15v10'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Nimaiki bo‘lgan bo‘lsam, Xudoning inoyati bilan bo‘ldim;
Uning menga ko‘rsatgan inoyati puchga chiqmadi,
zero men havoriylarning hammasidan ko‘proq
mehnat qildim.
Aslida mehnat qilgan o‘zim emas,
balki menga yor bo‘lgan Xudo inoyatidir.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-11'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 11 May 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='2' verse='15' id='Gn2v15'>
<text>Parvardigor Egamiz,
bu odam boqqa ishlov bersin,
parvarish qilsin,
deb uni Adan bog‘iga joylashtirdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 2:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='17' verse='15' id='J17v15'>
<intro>Iso ko‘zlarini osmonga tikib, dedi:</intro>
<text>Ey Muqaddas Ota!
Endi ularni dunyodan olishingni emas,
balki yovuz shaytondan saqlashingni so‘rayapman.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 17:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-12'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 12 May 2017</title>
<parol book='33' chapter='5' verse='4' id='Mch5v4'>
<text>O‘sha zot tinchlik o‘rnatuvchi bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Mixo 5:5-6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='2' verse='15' id='L2v15'>
<text>Farishtalar cho‘ponlar oldidan osmonga
qo‘tarilgan zamon,
cho‘ponlar bir–biriga dedilar:
— Qani, Baytlahmga boraylik!
Egamiz bizga aytgan voqea yuz
berganini ko‘raylik!</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 2:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-13'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 13 May 2017</title>
<parol book='54' chapter='6' verse='7' id='1T6v7-8'>
<text>Biz dunyoga hech narsa keltirmadik,
undan hech narsa olib ketolmasligimiz ham aniq.
Yeyish uchun rizq-ro‘z va kiyish uchun kiyim bo‘lsa,
shular bilan qanoat hosil qilaylik.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Timo‘tiy 6:7-8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='26' id='Mt6v26'>
<text>Qushlarga qaranglar:
ular na ekadi, na o‘radi, na omborga don yig‘adi.
Shunga qaramay, osmondagi Otangiz ularning rizqini beradi.
Sizlar esa ulardan ancha qadrlisizlar–ku!</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-14'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 14 May 2017</title>
<parol book='7' chapter='6' verse='23' id='Jdc6v23-24'>
<text>Egamiz:
— Tinchlan, — dedi Gido‘nga.
— Qo‘rqma, sen o‘lmaysan.
Gido‘n Egamizga atab bir qurbongoh qurib,
uning nomini: “Egamiz tinchlikdir”, deb atadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hakamlar 6:23-24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='1' verse='30' id='L1v30'>
<text>Farishta unga dedi:
— Maryam, qo‘rqma, sen Xudodan inoyat topding.</text>
<ref>Luqo 1:30</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-15'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 15 May 2017</title>
<parol book='18' chapter='16' verse='19' id='Job16v19'>
<text>Mana, hozir mening guvohim samodadir,
Mening himoyachim yuksakda o‘tiribdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ayub 16:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='88' verse='9' id='Ps88v9-10'>
<text>Qamalib qolganman, xalos bo‘la olmayman.
Ko‘zlarim nuri g‘amdan adoyi tamom bo‘ldi.
Ey Egam, har kun Senga iltijo qilaman,
Qo‘llarimni Sen tomon cho‘zaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 87:9-10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-16'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 16 May 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='9' id='J14v9'>
<text>— Filip, — dedi unga Iso,
— Men shuncha vaqtdan beri sizlar bilan birgaman.
Nahotki Meni tanimasang?!
Meni ko‘rgan odam Otani ko‘rgan bo‘ladi.
Shunday ekan, qanday qilib sen: “Otani bizga ko‘rsating”, deyapsan?</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 14:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='61' chapter='3' verse='18' id='2P3v18'>
<text>O‘z hayotingiz bilan Xudoni mamnun etinglar,
Rabbimiz va Najotkorimiz Iso Masihni
yanada yaqinroq tanib–bilinglar.
Hozirdan to abad Unga shon–sharaflar bo‘lsin!
Omin.</text>
<ref>2 Butrus 3:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-17'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 17 May 2017</title>
<parol book='59' chapter='4' verse='10' id='Jc4v10'>
<text>Egamiz oldida o‘zingizni past tutinglar,
shunda U sizlarni yuksaltiradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yoqub 4:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='18' verse='14' id='L18v14'>
<text>O‘zini o‘zi yuksaltirgan odam kamsitiladi,
o‘zini past olgan odam esa yuksaltiriladi.</text>
<ref>Luqo 18:14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-18'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 18 May 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='8' verse='4' id='Jr8v4'>
<text>Yiqilgan odam turmaydimi? !
Yo‘ldan adashgan ortiga qaytmaydimi? !</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 8:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='3' verse='2' id='Mt3v2'>
<text>Yahyo payg‘ambar odamlarga:
Tavba qilinglar,
chunki Osmon Shohligi yaqinlashdi!
— deb aytardi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 3:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-19'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 19 May 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='13' verse='33' id='Mt13v33'>
<text>Iso ularga boshqa bir masalni ham aytib berdi:
“Xudoning Shohligi xamirturushga o‘xshaydi.
Ayol bir bo‘lak xamirturushni uch tog‘ora unga qorsa ham,
hamma xamir oshadi.”</text>
<ref>Matto 13:33</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='4' verse='4' id='Act4v4'>
<text>Bu xabarni eshitganlarning ko‘pchiligi imonga keldi,
imonlilar soni besh mingtaga ko‘paydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 4:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-20'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 20 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='27' verse='14' id='Ps27v14'>
<text>Egamizga umid bog‘la,
Dadil bo‘l, yuragingga dalda ber,
Egamizga umid bog‘la!</text>
<ref>Zabur 26:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='4' verse='16' id='2K4v16'>
<text>Biz umidsizlanmaymiz.
Garchi zohiriy vujudimiz har qancha
xazon bo‘layotgan bo‘lsa-da,
botiniy vujudimiz kundan-kunga yangilanyapti.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 4:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-21'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 21 May 2017</title>
<parol book='52' chapter='5' verse='17' id='1Th5v17'>
<text>Tinmay ibodat qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 5:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='24' chapter='29' verse='13' id='Jr29v13-14'>
<text>Meni butun qalbingiz bilan izlasangizlar, topasizlar.
Ha, Meni topasizlar, — deb aytmoqda Egamiz.
— Men sizlarni yana farovonlikka erishtiraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 29:13-14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-22'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 22 May 2017</title>
<parol book='33' chapter='5' verse='3' id='Mch5v3'>
<intro>Kelajak hukmdor haqida bashorat:</intro>
<text>Egamizning qudrati ila
o‘sha hukmdor suruvini boqadi,
Egamiz Xudo O‘z ulug‘vorligi ila ularni boshqaradi.
Isroil xalqi xatarsiz yashaydi,
Axir, hukmdorining dovrug‘i butun dunyoga yoyiladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Mixo 5:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='2' verse='39' id='Act2v39'>
<intro>Havoriy Butrus e’lon qildi:</intro>
<text>Xudo sizlarga va bolalaringizga,
uzoqdagilarga,
Egamiz Xudo O‘ziga da’vat etganlarning
har biriga va’dasini bergan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 2:39</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-23'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 23 May 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='14' verse='9' id='R14v9'>
<text>Masih o‘liklarning hamda tiriklarning
Rabbiysi bo‘lish uchun o‘ldi va
o‘likdan tirildi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 14:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='1' verse='17' id='Ap1v17-18'>
<text>Qo‘rqma!
Men Birinchi va Oxirgiman. Barhayotman.
O‘lgan edim va mana, abadulabad tirikman.
O‘limning va O‘liklar diyorining kalitlari Mendadir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 1:17-18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-24'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 24 May 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='8' verse='58' id='1Rg8v58'>
<text>Egamizning yo‘lidan yurmoq uchun,
ko‘nglimizni O‘ziga rom qilsin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 8:58</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='2' verse='10' id='E2v10'>
<text>Axir biz Xudoning ijodimiz.
Xudo bizni xayrli ishlar qilishimiz uchun
Iso Masih orqali yaratdi,
bu ishlarni biz uchun azaldanoq
tayyorlab qo‘ygan edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 2:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-25'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 25 May 2017</title>
<parol book='62' chapter='3' verse='8' id='1J3v8'>
<text>Gunoh qiluvchi iblis zotidandir.
Chunki iblis azaldan gunoh qilib kelyapti.
Ammo Xudoning O‘g‘li iblisning ishlarini
barbod qilish uchun keldi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 3:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='26' id='1K15v26'>
<text>Shunda oxirgi dushman –
o‘lim ham barham topadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-26'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 26 May 2017</title>
<parol book='48' chapter='1' verse='22' id='G1v22-24'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Yahudiya o‘lkasidagi imonlilar jamoatlari
meni hali shaxsan tanimas edilar.
O‘sha imonlilar men haqimda faqat boshqalarning:
“U bir vaqtlar bizlarni quvg‘in qilib yurgan kishi edi.
Endi esa ilgari ildizi bilan quritmoqchi bo‘lgan imonni
o‘zi targ‘ib qilmoqda”, degan gaplarini eshitardilar
va men tufayli Xudoni ulug‘lar edilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Galatiyaliklar 1:22-24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='13' verse='6' id='1K13v6'>
<text>Sevgi nohaqlikka sevinmas,
aksincha, haqiqat ila shod bo‘lur.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 13:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-27'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 27 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='94' verse='9' id='Ps94v9'>
<text>Quloqni yaratgan eshitmaydimi? !
Ko‘zni ato etgan ko‘rmaydimi? !</text>
<ref>Zabur 93:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='121' verse='3' id='Ps121v3'>
<text>Qoqilishingga U yo‘l qo‘ymas,
U Posboningdir, aslo mudramas.</text>
<ref>Zabur 120:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-28'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 28 May 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='30' verse='20' id='Jr30v20'>
<text>Farzandlari oldingiday farovon hayot kechiradi,
Jamoasi oldimda mustahkam turadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 30:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='16' verse='18' id='Mt16v18'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Butrus, senga shuni aytay: sening isming qoya–ku!
Mana shu qoya ustiga Men O‘zimning jamoatimni quraman.
Hatto o‘lim shohligi ham jamoatimga bas kela olmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 16:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-29'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 29 May 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='34' verse='12' id='Ps34v12'>
<text>Keling, ey bolalar, tinglangiz meni,
O‘rgatayin men Egamizdan qo‘rqishni.</text>
<ref>Zabur 33:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='18' verse='17' id='L18v17'>
<text>Kim Xudoning Shohligini bola kabi qabul qilmasa,
unga hech qachon kirolmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 18:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-30'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 30 May 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='26' verse='15' id='Dt26v15'>
<text>Osmondagi muqaddas makoningdan bizga boq!
Ota–bobolarimizga ichgan qasamingga binoan,
bizga, Isroil xalqingga, baraka ber.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 26:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='16' verse='7' id='J16v7'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Mening ketishim sizlar uchun yaxshiroqdir.
Agar Men ketmasam, Homiy kelmaydi.
Agarda ketsam, Uni oldingizga yuboraman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 16:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-05-31'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 31 May 2017</title>
<parol book='27' chapter='2' verse='44' id='Dn2v44'>
<text>O‘sha davrda Samoviy Xudo
bitmas–tuganmas bir shohlik o‘rnatadi.
Hech kim uni yenga olmaydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Doniyor 2:44</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='18' verse='3' id='Mt18v3'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Agar sizlar o‘zgarmasangiz va
bolalarday bo‘lmasangiz,
hech qachon Osmon Shohligiga kira olmaysizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 18:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-01'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 1 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='12' verse='4' id='1K12v4-5'>
<text>Ruhiy in’omlar har xildir,
Ruh esa bittadir.
Xizmatlar har xildir,
Rabbimiz esa bittadir.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 12:4-5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='4' verse='7' id='E4v7'>
<text>Masih O‘z inoyatiga ko‘ra har birimizga
turli xil in’omlar bergan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 4:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-02'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 2 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='9' chapter='10' verse='6' id='1Sm10v6'>
<text>Egamiz Ruhi seni ham qamrab oladi.
Ular bilan birga sen ham jo‘shib
zikr tushasan
va butunlay boshqa odamga aylanasan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 10:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='24' verse='49' id='L24v49'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men sizlarga Otam va’da qilgan
Muqaddas Ruhni yuboraman.
Shuning uchun yuqoridan qudrat kelib
sizlarni qamrab olmaguncha,
shu shaharda qolinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 24:49</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-03'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 3 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='1' id='1K15v1'>
<text>Birodarlar, men sizlarga eslatmoqchiman:
o‘zim Injil Xushxabarini sizlarga yetkazgan edim,
sizlar esa uni tan olib,
unga qattiq umid bog‘ladingizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='52' chapter='2' verse='4' id='1Th2v4'>
<text>Xushxabarni ishonib topshirishga Xudo bizni loyiq topdi.
Shunday ekan, biz insonlarni mamnun qilaylik deb emas,
balki yuraklarimizni tekshiradigan Xudoni mamnun qilaylik,
deya ta’lim beramiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 2:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-04'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 4 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='7' verse='51' id='Act7v51'>
<intro>Stefan yahudiy ulamolariga:</intro>
<text>Sizlar o‘jar xalqsiz! Ey yuraklari,
quloqlari sunnat qilinmaganlar!
Sizlar ham, ota–bobolaringizga o‘xshab,
har doim Muqaddas Ruhga qarshi turasizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 7:51</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='3' verse='34' id='Prv3v34'>
<text>Egam mazax qiluvchilarni mazax qiladi,
kamtarga esa inoyat qiladi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 3:34</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-05'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 5 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='103' verse='8' id='Ps103v8'>
<text>Egamiz rahmdil, inoyatlidir,
Jahli tez chiqmaydi, sodiq sevgisi mo‘ldir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 102:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='6' verse='36' id='L6v36'>
<text>Otangiz rahmdil bo‘lgani kabi,
sizlar ham rahmdil bo‘linglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 6:36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-06'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 6 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='13' verse='10' id='R13v10'>
<text>O‘zgani yaxshi ko‘rgan odam unga yomonlik qilmaydi.
Shunday qilib, boshqalarni yaxshi ko‘rish Xudoning
qonunini to‘liq bajarish bilan barobardir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 13:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='3' chapter='19' verse='18' id='Lv19v18'>
<text>Qasos olmang, yurtdoshingizga qarshi kek saqlamang.
Aksincha, o‘zgani o‘zingizni sevganday seving.
Men Egangizman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Leviy 19:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-07'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 7 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='8' verse='34' id='R8v34'>
<text>Bizni kim mahkum qilar ekan?!
Axir, o‘lib, tirilgan,
Xudoning o‘ng tomonida turgan
Iso Masihning O‘zi biz uchun shafoat
qilmoqda–ku!</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 8:34</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='1' verse='3' id='H1v3'>
<text>O‘g‘il — Xudo shuhratining porlashi,
Xudo borlig‘ining aniq suratidir.
U O‘zining qudratli kalomi bilan koinotni
asrab turibdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 1:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-08'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 8 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='126' verse='1' id='Ps126v1'>
<text>Egamiz Quddusni yana farovonlikka erishtirganda,
Tush ko‘rayotgan odamlarga o‘xshar edik.</text>
<ref>Zabur 125:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='5' verse='10' id='R5v10'>
<text>Biz hali Uning dushmanlari bo‘lgan paytimizda,
Xudo O‘z O‘g‘lining o‘limi orqali
bizlarni O‘zi bilan yarashtirdi.
Biz endi Xudo bilan yarashgan ekanmiz,
albatta O‘g‘lining hayoti tufayli najot topamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 5:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-09'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 9 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='37' verse='14' id='Gn37v14'>
<text>Borib bil–chi,
akalaring tinch–omon yurishibdimikan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 37:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='6' verse='22' id='E6v22'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Bizning ahvolimizni sizlarga bildirsin,
sizlarga dalda bersin, deb Tixikni
sizlarning oldingizga yuboryapman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 6:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-10'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 10 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='10' verse='36' id='L10v36-37'>
<intro>Iso Masih ulamoga dedi:</intro>
<text>— Sizningcha, o‘sha uch odamdan qaysi biri qaroqchilar
qo‘liga tushgan odamning yaqini hisoblanadi?
Tafsirchi:
— Unga shafqat ko‘rsatgan odam–da, — deb javob berdi.
— Boring, siz ham shunday qiling! — dedi unga Iso.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 10:36-37</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='15' verse='2' id='R15v2'>
<text>Har birimiz o‘zganing manfaatini ko‘zlab,
unga dalda berish niyatida
uni mamnun qilish harakatida bo‘laylik.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 15:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-11'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 11 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='111' verse='2' id='Ps111v2'>
<text>Egamizning ishlari buyukdir,
Ulardan lazzat oluvchilar
ular haqda fikr yuritadilar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 110:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='13' verse='10' id='Mt13v10-11'>
<text>Shogirdlar kelib, Isodan so‘radilar:
— Nega odamlarga masallar bilan gapiryapsiz?
U shunday javob berdi:
— Osmon Shohligining sirlarini bilish ularga emas,
sizlarga berilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 13:10-11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-12'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 12 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='41' verse='2' id='Ps41v2'>
<text>Baxtlidir bechorani o‘ylaydiganlar,
Kulfatda qolganlarida Egamiz
ularni qutqaradi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 40:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='25' verse='34' id='Mt25v34'>
<text>Shundan keyin Shoh o‘ng tomonidagilarga aytadi:
— Ey Otamning barakasini olganlar, kelinglar!
Shohlikni meros qilib olinglar!
Bu shohlik olam yaratilgandayoq
sizlar uchun tayyorlab qo‘yilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 25:34</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-13'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 13 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='44' verse='3' id='Is44v3'>
<text>Chanqoq yerga Men suv beraman,
Qaqragan tuproqda irmoqlar oqizaman.
Naslingga Ruhimni beraman,
Zurriyoting ustiga O‘z barakamni yog‘diraman.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 44:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='45' verse='8' id='Is45v8'>
<text>Ey samolar, yuqoridan solihlik yog‘diring,
Ha, solihlik bulutlardan quyilsin.
Yer ochilib, najot kelib chiqsin,
Solihlik bilan birga yashnasin.
Men Egangizman! Men uni yaratganman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 45:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-14'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 14 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='60' chapter='2' verse='24' id='1P2v24'>
<text>Masih gunohlarimizni O‘ziga oldi,
a’zoi badani xochda azob chekdi.
Uning yaralaridan biz shifo topdik.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Butrus 2:24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='1' verse='7' id='E1v7'>
<text>Masihning to‘kilgan qoni orqali Xudo bizni kechirib,
gunohlarimizdan ozod qildi.
Shunday qilib, Xudo bizning hayotimizni to‘ldirgan
inoyati qanchalik boy ekanligini ko‘rsatdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 1:7-9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-15'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 15 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='14' verse='21' id='Jr14v21'>
<text>Noming haqi–hurmati bizni rad etma,
Ulug‘vor taxting turgan joyni xor qilma.
Biz bilan tuzgan ahdingni yodingda tut,
O‘tinamiz, ahdingni buzma.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 14:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='2' verse='13' id='2T2v13'>
<text>Agar biz sadoqatsizlik qilsak,
U yana sodiq qoladi,
Chunki O‘zini O‘zi inkor eta olmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 2:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-16'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 16 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='32' verse='1' id='Ps32v1'>
<text><em>Dovud qasidasi.</em>
Itoatsizligi kechirilganlar baxtlidir,
Egamiz kimning gunohidan o‘tgan bo‘lsa,
O‘sha inson baxtlidir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 31:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='130' verse='4' id='Ps130v4'>
<text>Hoy Egam, Sen kechirimlisan,
Shu bois Sendan qo‘rqamiz.</text>
<ref>Zabur 129:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-17'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 17 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='66' verse='10' id='Is66v10'>
<text>Ey Quddusni sevadiganlar,
Quddus bilan birga sevining,
Hammangiz u bilan birga shodlaning.
Ey Quddus uchun aza tutganlar,
U bilan birga xursand bo‘ling!</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 66:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='1' verse='24' id='2K1v24'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel yozgan :</intro>
<text>Biz go‘yo sizlarning imoningiz
ustidan hukmronlik o‘rnatayotganday bo‘lyapmiz.
Aslida biz quvonishingiz uchun sizlarga ko‘maklashmoqdamiz.
Chunki sizlar imonda mahkam turibsizlar.</text>
<ref>2 Korinfliklar 1:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-18'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 18 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='15' verse='17' id='Mc15v17-18'>
<text>Unga safsar to‘n kiydirishdi
va tikanlardan toj o‘rib boshiga qo‘yishdi.
— Yashavor, ey yahudiylarning Shohi!
— deb Uni qutlay boshlashdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 15:17-18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='15' verse='39' id='Mc15v39'>
<text>Isoning qarshisida turgan yuzboshi
Uning shu tarzda jon berganini ko‘rib:
Haqiqatan ham bu Odam Xudoning O‘g‘li ekan!
— dedi.</text>
<ref>Mark 15:39</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-19'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 19 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='28' chapter='6' verse='1' id='Hos6v1'>
<text>Bu xalq shunday deydi:
Kelinglar, Egamizga qaytaylik!
U bizni tilka–pora qildi,
Shifoni ham O‘zi beradi.
Bizni yarador qildi,
Yaralarimizni O‘zi bog‘laydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ho‘shiyo 6:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='9' verse='14' id='R9v14-15'>
<text>Xudo adolatsizmi? Yo‘q, aslo!
Xudo Musoga:
“Marhamat qiladiganimga marhamat qilaman,
shafqat qiladiganimga shafqat qilaman”, deb aytgan.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 9:14-15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-20'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 20 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='14' verse='13' id='L14v13-14'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Ziyofat berganingizda, kambag‘al–qashshoqlarni, cho‘loq,
shollarni, ko‘rlarni taklif qiling. Shunda baxtli bo‘lasiz.
Chunki ular qilgan yaxshiligingizni qaytara olmasalar–da,
solihlar tirilgan zamonda buning savobini ko‘rasiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 14:13-14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='13' verse='2' id='H13v2'>
<text>Mehmondo‘stlikni unutmanglar.
Zero, mehmondo‘st bo‘lgan ba’zi odamlar
o‘zlari bilmagan holda farishtalarni mehmon qilishgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 13:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-21'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 21 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='16' verse='16' id='Mc16v16'>
<text>Kimki Xushxabarga ishonib,
suvga cho‘mdirilsa, najot topadi.
Ishonmagan esa mahkum bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 16:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='5' verse='35' id='Mc5v35-36'>
<text>Iso shunday deb turgan ham ediki,
sinagoga oqsoqolining uyidan odamlar kelib unga:
— Qizingiz o‘ldi, nega yana Ustozni ovora qilyapsiz?
— dedilar.
Iso bu so‘zlarni eshitib qolib, sinagoga oqsoqoliga:
— Qo‘rqmang, faqat ishoning, — dedi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 5:35-36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-22'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 22 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='15' verse='51' id='1K15v51'>
<text>Hammamiz o‘lmaymiz-u,
ammo hammamiz o‘zgarib ketamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 15:51</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='24' verse='31' id='Mt24v31'>
<text>Karnayning baland sadosi ostida
U farishtalarini yerning to‘rt tomoniga yuboradi.
Ular dunyoning bir burchagidan boshqa burchagigacha
tanlangan odamlarni to‘plab olishadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 24:31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-23'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 23 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='38' chapter='1' verse='3' id='Zch1v3'>
<text>Menga qaytinglar,
demoqda Sarvari Olam.
Shunda Men ham sizlarga qaytaman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Zakariyo 1:2-3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='29' verse='1' id='Prv29v1'>
<text>Tanbeh olsa ham o‘jarligicha qoladigan odam
birdaniga halokatga uchraydi,
shifo topmaydi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 29:1</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-24'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 24 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='59' chapter='4' verse='17' id='Jc4v17'>
<text>Qilishingiz kerak bo‘lgan yaxshi ishni bila turib,
qilmasangiz gunoh bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Yoqub 4:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='3' verse='17' id='1J3v17'>
<text>Agar o‘zimizga to‘q bo‘lib turib,
muhtojlikda yashayotgan birodarimizni ko‘rsak–u,
unga yordam bermay yuragimizni tosh qilsak,
qanday qilib bizda Xudoning sevgisi joy oladi?</text>
<ref>1 Yuhanno 3:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-25'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 25 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='3' verse='17' id='1K3v17'>
<text>Xudoning ma’badi muqaddasdir;
bu ma’bad esa sizlarsiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 3:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='2' verse='19' id='E2v19-20'>
<text>Sizlar endi begona ham, kelgindi ham emassizlar,
balki Xudoning aziz xalqi qatoridasiz,
Uning xonadoni a’zosi bo‘ldingizlar.
Sizlar xuddi bir binodaysizlar.
Bu binoning asosi havoriylaru payg‘ambarlardir.
Binoning tamal toshi esa Iso Masihning O‘zidir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 2:19-20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-26'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 26 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='147' verse='14' id='Ps147v14'>
<text>Shohligingga U tinchlik ato qiladi,
Bug‘doyning eng yaxshisi bilan to‘ydiradi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 147:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='38' chapter='9' verse='8' id='Zch9v8'>
<intro>Rabbimiz dedi:</intro>
<text>Bosqinchilardan asray, deb
Men O‘zim uyimni qo‘riqlayman.</text>
<ref>Zakariyo 9:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-27'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 27 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='5' verse='9' id='Act5v9'>
<text>Butrus Safiraga dedi:
Nima uchun sizlar Egamizning Ruhini sinashga
qaror qildingizlar? Ana, eringni dafn qilgan
odamlar eshikdan kirib kelishyapti.
Endi ular seni ham olib chiqadilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 5:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='4' verse='7' id='Mt4v7'>
<text>Egang Xudoni sinama, deb ham yozilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 4:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-28'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 28 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='19' verse='12' id='Ps19v12'>
<text>Ey Egam,
qoidalaring menga, O‘z qulingga o‘git beradi,
Qoidalaringga itoat etganlar buyuk mukofot oladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 18:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='63' chapter='1' verse='8' id='2J1v8'>
<text>Shunday ekan, ogoh bo‘linglar!
Mukofotingizni to‘liq olish uchun,
Masihga bo‘lgan haqiqiy imoningizni
mahkam tutinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Yuhanno 8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-29'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 29 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='2' verse='41' id='Act2v41'>
<text>Butrusning aytgan xabariga ishonganlar
suvga cho‘mdirildi. O‘sha kuni imonlilar
soni uch mingtaga ko‘paydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 2:41</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='51' chapter='2' verse='12' id='Kol2v12'>
<text>Suvga cho‘mdirilish orqali
Masih bilan birga ko‘mildingiz.
Masihni o‘likdan tiriltirgan Xudoning
qudratiga bo‘lgan imoningiz tufayli
Masih bilan birga tirildingiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 2:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-06-30'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 30 Iyun 2017</title>
<parol book='50' chapter='4' verse='13' id='Ph4v13'>
<text>Menga kuch–quvvat beradigan Iso Masihning
madadi bilan har narsani qila olaman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Filipiliklar 4:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='18' verse='30' id='Ps18v30'>
<text>Ey Xudoyim!
Senga suyanib lashkarni yo‘q qilaman,
Senga suyanib devorlardan oshib o‘taman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 17:30</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-01'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 1 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='36' chapter='3' verse='14' id='Zph3v14-15'>
<text>Ey Isroil xalqi, sevinch ila hayqiring!
Ey Quddus aholisi, kuylang!
Ey Sion ahli, butun qalbingizdan shodlaning!
Egamiz sizlarni jazolab bo‘ldi,
Dushmanlaringizni U quvib yubordi.</text>
<ref>Safoniyo 3:14-15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='9' chapter='30' verse='6' id='1Sm30v6'>
<text>Dovud yomon ahvolda qoldi,
chunki har bir odam o‘g‘illari, qizlari uchun qayg‘urar,
“Dovudni toshbo‘ron qilamiz”, deyishardi.
Lekin Dovud o‘z Egasi Xudodan madad oldi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 30:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-02'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 2 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='18' chapter='13' verse='9' id='Job13v9'>
<text>Qilayotganlaringizni U tekshirib ko‘rsa, yaxshi bo‘ladimi?
Yoki insonni aldaganday Uni ham aldaysizlarmi?!</text>
<ref>Ayub 13:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='48' chapter='6' verse='7' id='G6v7'>
<text>O‘zlaringni aldamanglar! Xudoni laqillatib bo‘lmaydi.
Inson nima eksa, shuni o‘rib oladi.</text>
<ref>Galatiyaliklar 6:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-03'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 3 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='20' chapter='20' verse='9' id='Prv20v9'>
<text>Qalbimni tozaladim, gunohimdan xoliman,
deb kim ayta oladi?!</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 20:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='8' verse='2' id='R8v2'>
<text>Hayot ato etuvchi Ruhning qonun–qoidasi
Iso Masih orqali meni gunohdan
va o‘limga yetaklaydigan qonundan ozod qildi.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 8:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-04'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 4 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='40' verse='3' id='Is40v3'>
<text>Bir ovoz shunday hayqirmoqda:
Sahroda Egamizga yo‘l hozirlang,
Cho‘lda Xudoyimizga to‘g‘ri yo‘l oching.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 40:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='30' id='J3v30'>
<intro>Havoriy Yuhanno dedi:</intro>
<text>Masih yuksalishi, men esa pasayishim kerak.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 3:30</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-05'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 5 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='4' verse='3' id='Jr4v3'>
<text>Egamiz shunday deb aytmoqda:
Yeringizni shudgor qiling,
Tikanlar orasiga urug‘ sepmang.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 4:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='28' chapter='10' verse='12' id='Hos10v12'>
<text>O‘zingiz uchun solihlik urug‘ini eking,
Cheksiz sevgini o‘rib oling.
Haydalmagan yeringizga ishlov bering.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ho‘shiyo 10:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-06'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 6 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='1' verse='5' id='Act1v5'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Yahyo odamlarni suvga cho‘mdirar edi,
sizlar esa yaqin kunlarda
Muqaddas Ruhga cho‘mdirilasizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 1:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='29' chapter='3' verse='1' id='Joel3v1'>
<text>Egamiz demoqda:
O‘z Ruhimni yog‘dirman har bir inson ustiga,
Vahiylar keladi yigitlaringizga.
Bashorat qilurlar sizning o‘g‘il–qizlaringiz.
Karomatli tushlar ko‘rurlar qariyalaringiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yo‘il 2:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-07'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 7 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='28' chapter='2' verse='1' id='Hos2v1'>
<text>Shunday vaqtlar keladiki,
Isroil xalqi dengizdagi qum kabi bo‘ladi,
ularni na sanab, na o‘lchab bo‘ladi.
Ularga: ‘Xalqim emas’, deb aytilgan bo‘lsa, kelajakda ular:
‘Barhayot Xudoning bolalari’, deb ataladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ho‘shiyo 1:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='5' verse='12' id='1J5v12'>
<text>Kim Xudoning O‘g‘liga ega bo‘lsa,
hayotga egadir.
Xudoning O‘g‘liga ega bo‘lmagan
odamda esa hayot yo‘q.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 5:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-08'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 8 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='40' verse='18' id='Ps40v18_I'>
<text>Men esa g‘arib, bechoraman,
Ey Rabbiy, men haqimda o‘ylagin,
Madadkorim, najotkorim O‘zingsan,
Kechikmagin, ey Xudoyim!</text>
<ref>Zabur 39:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='12' verse='11' id='L12v11-12'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Sizlarni sinagogalarga,
boshliqlar va hokimlar oldiga
olib kelganlarida:
O‘zimizni qanday himoya qilamiz,
nima aytamiz, deb xavotir olmanglar.
Nima deb gapirishingizni o‘sha vaqtda sizga Muqaddas Ruh o‘rgatadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 12:11-12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-09'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 9 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='5' verse='26' id='L5v26'>
<text>Hamma hayratga tushib, Xudoni ulug‘ladi.
Ular qo‘rquv ichra:
“Bugun aql bovar qilmaydigan
hodisani ko‘rdik”, deb aytardilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 5:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='12' verse='14' id='Act12v14-15'>
<text>Qamoqdan qutulgan Butrusning ovozini qiz tanigach,
shunchalik xursand bo‘lib ketdiki,
darvozani ochish o‘rniga, ichkariga yugurib kirdi–da,
— Butrus darvoza oldida turibdi, — deb e’lon qildi.
— Aqlingni yeb qo‘yibsan, — dedi ular qizga.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 12:14-15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-10'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 10 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='22' chapter='8' verse='4' id='Ct8v4'>
<text>Ey Quddus qizlari, va’da beringlar,
Vaqt–soati kelmaguncha,
Sevgini qo‘zg‘atmang, uyg‘otmang.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning go‘zal qo‘shig‘i 8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='37' verse='4' id='Ps37v4'>
<text>Egamizni o‘zingning shodliging deb bil,
Ko‘nglingdagi orzularingga U yetkazadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 36:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-11'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 11 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='23' verse='9' id='Ex23v9'>
<text>Musofirga zulm qilmanglar.
O‘zlaringiz Misrda musofir bo‘lgan edingizlar,
shu bois musofirning ahvolini bilasizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 23:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='10' verse='24' id='1K10v24'>
<text>Har kim o‘zining emas,
o‘zganing manfaatini ko‘zlasin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 10:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-12'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 12 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='24' verse='13' id='Mt24v13'>
<text>Oxirigacha bardosh bergan najot topadi.</text>
<ref>Matto 24:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='3' verse='6' id='H3v6'>
<text>Masih sodiq O‘g‘il edi.
Unga Xudoning xonadonini boshqarish topshirildi.
Xudoning xonadoni esa bizmiz.
Biz faqat jasur bo‘lib,
umidimizni mahkam tutishimiz kerak.
Axir, biz bu umidimiz bilan faxrlanamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 3:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-13'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 13 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='44' chapter='19' verse='11' id='Act19v11'>
<text>Xudo Pavlus orqali g‘aroyib
mo‘jizalar ko‘rsatar edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 19:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='18' chapter='9' verse='10' id='Job9v10'>
<text>Inson aqli bovar qilmaydigan
buyuk ishlar qiladi Xudo,
U qilgan mo‘jizalarning son–sanog‘i yo‘qdir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ayub 9:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-14'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 14 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='39' verse='19' id='Gn39v19'>
<text>Po‘tifar xotinidan Yusufning qilgan
muomalasini eshitgach, g‘azablandi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 39:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='2' verse='23' id='1P2v23'>
<text>Iso haqorat qilinganda hech kimga haqorat bilan javob qaytarmadi,
azob chekkanda hech kimga tahdid qilmadi.
Faqat odilona hukm qiladigan Xudoga O‘zini topshirdi.</text>
<ref>1 Butrus 2:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-15'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 15 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='36' verse='29' id='Ez36v29'>
<text>Men sizlarni barcha nopokliklardan
xalos qilaman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 36:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='66' verse='10' id='Ps66v10'>
<text>Ey Xudo, Sen bizni sinading,
Kumushni tozalaganday bizni tozalading.</text>
<ref>Zabur 65:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-16'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 16 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='39' chapter='3' verse='6' id='Ml3v6'>
<text>Sarvari Olam shunday deydi:
Ey Yoqub o‘g‘lonlari, Men Egangizman.
Men hech qachon o‘zgarmayman!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Malaki 3:6-7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='53' chapter='3' verse='3' id='2Th3v3'>
<text>Rabbimiz Iso sadoqatlidir.
U sizlarni kuchga to‘ldirib,
yovuz shaytondan himoya qiladi.</text>
<ref>2 Salonikaliklar 3:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-17'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 17 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='1' verse='29' id='Dt1v29-30'>
<text>Vahimaga tushmanglar, ulardan qo‘rqmanglar.
Egangiz Xudoning O‘zi oldingizda yuradi.
Ko‘zingiz oldida Misrda jang qilganday,
sizlar uchun jang qiladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 1:29-30</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='16' verse='33' id='J16v33'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men tufayli xotirjam bo‘lishingiz uchun
bularni sizlarga aytdim.
Dunyoda qayg‘u–alam chekasizlar.
Lekin dadil bo‘linglar, Men dunyoni yengdim.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 16:33</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-18'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 18 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='76' id='Ps119v76'>
<text>Men, O‘z qulingga bergan va’dangga ko‘ra,
Sodiq sevging menga tasalli bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:76</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='2' verse='25' id='L2v25'>
<text>Quddusda Shimo‘n degan bir odam bor edi.
U solih, taqvodor odam bo‘lib,
Isroilning najot topishini intizor bo‘lib kutar edi.
Muqaddas Ruh unga yor edi.</text>
<ref>Luqo 2:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-19'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 19 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='10' verse='24' id='Jr10v24'>
<text>Ey Egam, meni jahl ustida jazolamagin.
Adolating ila haq yo‘lga solgin,
Aks holda meni yo‘q qilib yuborasan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 10:24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='3' verse='12' id='Prv3v12'>
<text>Ota yaxshi ko‘rgan farzandini jazolagandek,
Xudo ham sevganini jazolaydi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 3:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-20'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 20 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='6' chapter='21' verse='45' id='Jos21v45'>
<text>Egamiz Isroil xalqiga bergan
yaxshi va’dalarning hammasi ro‘yobga chiqdi,
birortasi ham bajarilmay qolmadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yoshua 21:45</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='25' verse='1' id='Is25v1'>
<text>Ey Egam, Sen mening Xudoyimsan.
Sen ajoyib ishlar qilgansan,
Men Seni sharaflayman.
Qadim davrlardan rejalar tuzgansan,
Ular sadoqatli va ishonchlidir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 25:1</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-21'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 21 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='47' chapter='8' verse='9' id='2K8v9'>
<text>Sizlar Rabbimiz Iso Masihning inoyatini bilasizlar:
U boy bo‘la turib, kambag‘alligim tufayli boy bo‘linglar,
deb sizlar uchun kambag‘allashdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 8:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='5' verse='19' id='2K5v19'>
<text>Xudo Masih vujudida bo‘lib dunyoni O‘zi bilan yarashtirdi,
odamlarning gunohlarini hisobga olmadi.
Bu yarashish to‘g‘risidagi xabarni yetkazishni esa bizga topshirdi.</text>
<ref>2 Korinfliklar 5:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-22'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 22 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='34' verse='7' id='Ps34v7'>
<text>Bu bechora iltijosin Egamiz eshitdi,
Barcha uqubatlardan uni qutqardi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 33:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='91' verse='15' id='Ps91v15'>
<intro>Rabbimiz aytadi:</intro>
<text>U iltijo qilganda Men javob beraman,
Og‘ir kunlarida u bilan birga bo‘laman,
Uni qutqarib, unga izzat ko‘rsataman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 90:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-23'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 23 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='21' verse='16' id='Ex21v16'>
<text>Kimki birortasini o‘g‘irlab,
o‘g‘irlagan odamni sotib yuborsa,
yoki hali ham ushlab turgan bo‘lsa,
o‘shaning jazosi o‘limdir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 21:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='6' verse='23' id='R6v23'>
<text>Gunohning evazi – o‘lim,
Xudoning in’omi esa –
Rabbimiz Iso Masih orqali beriladigan
abadiy hayotdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 6:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-24'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 24 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='23' id='Mt5v23-24'>
<text>Siz ehsoningizni qurbongohga olib kelganingizda,
birodaringiz nimadandir sizdan xafa ekanligi
yodingizga tushsa,
ehsoningizni qurbongoh oldida qoldiring.
Birinchi navbatda borib,
birodaringiz bilan yarashing,
keyin kelib, ehsoningizni nazr qiling.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:23-24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='3' chapter='19' verse='17' id='Lv19v17'>
<text>Dilingizda birodaringizga qarshi gina qilmang.
Qo‘shningizning aybini ochiq yuziga soling,
shunda siz uning aybi uchun jazoga tortilmaysiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Leviy 19:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-25'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 25 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='15' verse='27' id='J15v27'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Sizlar ham guvohlik berasizlar,
chunki boshdanoq Men bilan birga bo‘lgansizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 15:27</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='26' verse='16' id='Act26v16'>
<intro>Rabbimiz Havoriy Pavelga dedi:</intro>
<text>Seni O‘zimning xizmatkorim qilib
tayinlash maqsadida senga zohir bo‘ldim.
Sen Meni ko‘rganing va Men senga
ko‘rsatadiganlarim to‘g‘risida guvohlik berasan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 26:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-26'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 26 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='13' verse='5' id='1K13v5'>
<text>Sevgi beboshlik qilmas,
xudbinlik qilmas,
achchiqlanmas, kek saqlamas.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 13:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='48' chapter='5' verse='14' id='G5v14'>
<text>Axir, qonun:
“O‘zgani o‘zingizni sevganday seving”,
degan gapda mujassam bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Galatiyaliklar 5:14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-27'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 27 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='53' chapter='1' verse='11' id='2Th1v11'>
<text>Xudoyimiz sizni O‘z chaqirig‘iga loyiq deb topsin,
O‘z qudrati bilan sizlarning barcha
yaxshi niyatlaringizni ro‘yobga chiqarsin,
imon bilan qilgan ishlaringizni amalga oshirsin,
deb biz doim sizlar uchun ibodat qilamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Salonikaliklar 1:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='25' verse='21' id='Mt25v21'>
<text>Xo‘jayin xizmatkoriga:
— Barakalla! Sen yaxshi va ishonchli xizmatkorsan! — debdi.
— Kichik ishda ishonchimni oqlaganing uchun,
senga katta ishlarni ishonib topshiraman.
Kel, mening xursandchiligimga sherik bo‘l.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 25:21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-28'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 28 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='14' id='J14v14'>
<text>Sizlar Mening nomim bilan so‘ragan
har qanday narsani bajo keltiraman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 14:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='59' chapter='1' verse='5' id='Jc1v5'>
<text>Agar birortangizga donolik yetishmasa,
Xudodan so‘rang, U beradi.
Chunki so‘raganlarning hammasiga Xudo
saxovat bilan, beminnat beradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yoqub 1:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-29'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 29 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='3' chapter='19' verse='34' id='Lv19v34'>
<text>Unga o‘z yurtdoshingizday qarang.
Musofirni o‘zingizni sevganday seving,
chunki sizlar ham Misr yurtida musofir edingizlar.
Men Egangiz Xudoman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Leviy 19:34</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='22' verse='39' id='Mt22v39'>
<text>O‘zgani o‘zingizni sevganday seving.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 22:39</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-30'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 30 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='48' chapter='5' verse='25' id='G5v25'>
<text>Ruh hayotimiz manbayi ekan,
endi Ruhning yetakchiligi ostida hayot
kechirishimiz lozim.</text>
<ref>Injil, Galatiyaliklar 5:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='6' verse='11' id='R6v11'>
<text>O‘zingizni gunoh oldida o‘lik deb hisoblang.
Endi Iso Masih tufayli
Xudoga shuhrat keltirib yashashingiz kerak.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 6:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-07-31'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 31 Iyul 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='59' verse='1' id='Is59v1'>
<text>Nima, Egamizning qo‘li qisqami?
Qutqarolmasa!
Qulog‘i og‘irmi? Eshitmay qolsa!</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 59:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='10' verse='10' id='J10v10'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>O‘g‘ri faqat o‘g‘irlash, bo‘g‘izlash, barbod qilish uchun keladi.
Men esa ularga hayot, farovon hayot berish uchun kelganman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 10:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-01'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 1 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='23' verse='1' id='Ps23v1'>
<text>Dovud sanosi.
Egam Mening cho‘ponimdir.
Muhtojlik ko‘rmasman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 22:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='5' chapter='2' verse='7' id='Dt2v7_V'>
<text>Men, Egangiz Xudo,
qirq yildan beri sizlar bilan birgaman,
sizlar hech qanday kamchilik ko‘rmadingizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 2:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-02'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 2 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='6' chapter='1' verse='9' id='Jos1v9'>
<text>Dadil va botir bo‘l,
vahimaga tushma, qo‘rqma,
qayerga borsang ham, Men, Egang Xudo,
sen bilan birga bo‘laman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yoshua 1:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='10' verse='28' id='Mt10v28'>
<text>Tanani o‘ldirib, jonni o‘ldira olmaydiganlardan qo‘rqmanglar.
Xudodan qo‘rqinglar!
Chunki U jonni ham, tanani ham do‘zaxda halok etishga qodir.</text>
<ref>Matto 10:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-03'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 3 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='71' verse='16' id='Ps71v16'>
<text>Qudratli ishlaringni madh qilaman,
ey Egam Rabbiy,
Yolg‘iz Sening odilligingni madh qilaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 70:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='24' verse='10' id='Ps24v10'>
<text>U ulug‘vor Shoh kim ekan?
Sarvari Olamdir U.
Uning O‘zi ulug‘vor Shohdir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 23:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-04'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 4 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='20' chapter='21' verse='2' id='Prv21v2'>
<text>Odamning qilmishlari o‘zining nazarida to‘g‘ri,
ammo Egamiz yuraklarni sinaydi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 21:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='8' verse='36' id='Mc8v36'>
<text>Agar inson butun dunyoni egallab olsa–yu,
o‘z jonidan mahrum bo‘lsa,
bundan unga nima foyda?!</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 8:36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-05'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 5 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='12' verse='24' id='1K12v24-25'>
<text>Xudo badanni muvofiqlashtirib yaratdi,
yetishmagan uzvga alohida e’tibor berdi.
Shu tariqa badanda bo‘linish bo‘lmaydi,
lekin butun uzvlar bir-biriga
bir xil g‘amxo‘rlik qiladilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 12:24-25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='20' chapter='14' verse='31' id='Prv14v31'>
<text>Kambag‘alga zulm qilgan ularni Yaratganni tahqirlagan,
muhtojga yordam bergan esa Xudoni ulug‘lagan bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning Hikmatlari 14:31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-06'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 6 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='15' verse='18' id='Jr15v18'>
<text>Nega mening dardim zo‘rayyapti?
Nega og‘ir yaram tuzalmayapti?
Nahotki yozda qurigan buloq kabi
Umidlarimni barbod qilsang? !</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 15:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='12' verse='10' id='2K12v10'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel yozgan:</intro>
<text>Masih uchun zaifliklarga, ozorlarga, muhtojliklarga,
ta’qib va siquvlarga yo‘liqqanimda, qanoat qilaman.
Chunki zaif bo‘lsam, qudratim oshar ekan.</text>
<ref>2 Korinfliklar 12:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-07'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 7 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='51' chapter='1' verse='18' id='Kol1v18'>
<text>Masih jamoatning boshidir,
Jamoat Masihning tanasidir.
Hamma narsaning ibtidosi Masihdir,
U hammadan ustun bo‘lishi uchun
Birinchi bo‘lib o‘likdan tiriltirilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 1:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='4' verse='19' id='1J4v19'>
<text>Biz sevamiz,
chunki Xudo bizni birinchi bo‘lib sevdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 4:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-08'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 8 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='74' verse='21' id='Ps74v21'>
<text>Mazlum sharmandalikka duchor bo‘lmasin,
Faqiru bechora Senga hamdu sano aytsin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 73:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='8' verse='47' id='L8v47'>
<text>Nazardan chetda qola olmasligini bilib,
ayol titragancha Isoning oldiga keldi.
Uning oyoqlari ostiga o‘zini tashlab,
butun xalq oldida nima sababdan Isoga qo‘lini tekkizganini va
qo‘l tekkizgan zahoti shifo topganini aytib berdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 8:47</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-09'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 9 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='4' verse='10' id='Dt4v10'>
<text>Mening huzurimga xalqni yig‘.
Ular so‘zlarimni eshitib,
yer yuzida butun umrlari davomida
Mendan qo‘rqishni o‘rgansinlar,
bolalariga ham o‘rgatsinlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 4:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='19' verse='5' id='Ap19v5'>
<text>Ey Xudoyimizning barcha qullari,
Undan qo‘rquvchi kattayu kichiklar,
Unga hamdu sano aytinglar!</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 19:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-10'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 10 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='6' verse='5' id='Dt6v5'>
<text>Egangiz Xudoni butun qalbingiz bilan,
jonu dilingiz bilan,
butun vujudingiz bilan sevinglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 6:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='6' chapter='23' verse='11' id='Jos23v11'>
<text>Doimo chin dildan
Egangiz Xudoni sevinglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yoshua 23:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-11'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 11 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='12' verse='6' id='1K12v6-7'>
<text>Ruhiy ta’sirlar har xildir,
lekin hammada har qanday ta’sirni
vujudga keltirgan yagona Xudodir.
Muqaddas Ruh umumiy manfaat uchun
har kimda alohida faoliyat ko‘rsatadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 12:6-7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='12' verse='5' id='R12v5-6'>
<text>Biz — Masihga tegishli bo‘lganlar,
bir tanani tashkil qilamiz.
Har birimiz har xil a’zolar bo‘lib,
bir–birimizga bog‘liqmiz.
Bizga berilgan inoyat bo‘yicha har
birimizning har xil in’omlarimiz bor.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 12:5-6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-12'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 12 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='27' chapter='4' verse='32' id='Dn4v32'>
<text>Yerdagi insonlar Xudoyi Taoloning
nazdida hech narsadaydir,
Insonlaru malaklarga U hukmini o‘tkazgaydir.
Biror kimsa Unga bas kela olmas,
“Nima qilyapsan?” — deb so‘rashga jur’at etmas.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Doniyor 4:32</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='11' verse='17' id='Act11v17'>
<intro>Bytpyc dedi:</intro>
<text>Biz Rabbimiz Iso Masihga imon keltirganimizda,
Xudo bizga bergan in’omni
yot xalqlarga ham bergan bo‘lsa,
men kim bo‘libmanki, Xudoga qarshilik qilsam?!</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 11:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-13'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 13 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='23' verse='39' id='Mt23v39'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Egamiz nomi bilan keladigan inson
baraka topsin, — deb aytmaguningizcha,
Meni ko‘rmaysizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 23:39</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='1' verse='7' id='Ap1v7'>
<text>Ana, Masih bulutlarda kelyapti!
Har bir ko‘z Uni ko‘radi,
Hatto Unga nayza sanchganlar ham
Unga ko‘z tikadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 1:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-14'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 14 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='14' chapter='36' verse='16' id='2Chr36v16'>
<text>Ular Xudoning elchilarini haqorat qilib,
Xudoning so‘zlaridan nafratlandilar,
payg‘ambarlarni masxara qildilar.
Oxiri Egamiz O‘z xalqidan shu qadar g‘azablandiki,
ular najotsiz qoldilar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Solnomalar 36:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='3' verse='3' id='R3v3-4'>
<text>Ularning ba’zilari ishonmagan bo‘lsa,
nima bo‘pti? Ularning ishonmaganligi
Xudoning sadoqatini bekor qiladimi?
Yo‘q, aslo!</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 3:3-4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-15'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 15 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='9' verse='6' id='L9v6'>
<text>Havoriylar ketdilar.
Qishloqma–qishloq yurib,
hamma yoqda Xushxabarni e’lon qildilar,
xastalarga shifo berdilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 9:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='5' verse='42' id='Act5v42'>
<text>Ular har kuni Ma’bad hovlisida
va odamlarning uylarida ta’lim berardilar.
Isoning Masih ekani to‘g‘risidagi Xushxabarni
va’z qilishda davom etaverdilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 5:42</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-16'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 16 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='58' chapter='13' verse='5' id='H13v5'>
<text>Pulga ko‘ngil bog‘lamanglar.
Bori bilan qanoatlaninglar.
Zero, Xudo: “Sizlarni tashlab ketmayman,
sizlarni tark etmayman”, — deb aytgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 13:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='4' verse='19' id='Mc4v19'>
<text>Bu dunyoning tashvishlari, boylikka o‘chlik
va boshqa havaslar ularning yuraklariga kirib,
Xudoning kalomini bo‘g‘ib qo‘yadi, kalom esa samarasiz qoladi.</text>
<ref>Mark 4:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-17'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 17 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='23' verse='3' id='Ps23v3'>
<text>U O‘zining nomi haqi–hurmati
Meni to‘g‘ri so‘qmoqlardan yetaklaydi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 22:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='2' verse='25' id='1P2v25'>
<text>Ilgari sizlar adashib yurgan
cho‘ponsiz qo‘ylarga o‘xshar edingizlar,
endi esa jonlaringizning Posboni
bo‘lgan Cho‘ponga qaytib keldingizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Butrus 2:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-18'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 18 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='57' verse='8' id='Ps57v8'>
<text>Ey Xudo, yuragim Senga sodiq,
Ha, yuragim Senga sodiqdir!
Seni kuylab, qo‘shiq aytaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 56:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='147' verse='1' id='Ps147v1'>
<text>Egamizga hamdu sanolar bo‘lsin!
Naqadar yaxshidir Xudoyimizni tarannum etmoq!
Naqadar lazzatli, munosib
Unga hamdu sano aytmoq!</text>
<ref>Zabur 146:1</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-19'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 19 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='3' verse='9' id='1Rg3v9'>
<intro>Shoh Sulaymon ibodat qildi:</intro>
<text>Endi xalqingga shohlik qilishim uchun
menga aql–idrok berginki,
yaxshilik bilan yomonlikning farqiga borayin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 3:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='51' chapter='3' verse='2' id='Kol3v2'>
<text>Fikringiz yer yuzidagi emas,
samodagi narsalar bilan band bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Kolosaliklar 3:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-20'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 20 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='8' verse='10' id='Ps8v10'>
<text>Ey Egam, bizning Rabbimiz!
Butun yer yuzida Sening noming ulug‘vordir!</text>
<ref>Zabur 8:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='47' chapter='4' verse='15' id='2K4v15'>
<text>Bularning hammasi sizlar uchun sodir bo‘lmoqda,
toki Xudoning inoyati yana ko‘pdan-ko‘p odamlarga o‘tsin,
shu tariqa Xudoning hamdu sanosi yanada oshib,
tillardan tushmaydigan bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 4:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-21'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 21 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='5' verse='12' id='Ps5v12'>
<text>Senda panoh topganlarning hammasi sevinsin,
To abad shodlikdan ular kuylasin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 5:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='1' verse='6' id='1P1v6'>
<text>Hozir turli sinovlar tufayli
qisqa vaqt qiynalayotgan bo‘lsangiz ham, quvoninglar.</text>
<ref>1 Butrus 1:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-22'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 22 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='21' verse='17' id='J21v17'>
<text>Butrus Isoga dedi:
Rabbim! Siz hamma narsani bilasiz,
men Sizni yaxshi ko‘rishimni ham bilasiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 21:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='11' chapter='8' verse='39' id='1Rg8v39'>
<text>Jamiki inson bolasining ko‘nglidagini
yolg‘iz Sen bilasan, xolos.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 8:39-40</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-23'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 23 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='150' verse='2' id='Ps150v2'>
<text>Qudratli ishlari uchun
Unga hamdu sanolar bo‘lsin,
Tengsiz buyukligi uchun madhiyalar bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 150:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='10' chapter='7' verse='22' id='2Sm7v22'>
<text>Naqadar ulug‘vorsan, ey, Egamiz Rabbiy!
Senga o‘xshagan boshqa xudo haqida
hech qachon eshitmaganmiz,
Sening aslo o‘xshashing yo‘q,
Sendan o‘zga Xudo yo‘q!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Shohlar 7:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-24'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 24 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='80' verse='15' id='Ps80v15-16'>
<text>Ey Parvardigori Olam!
Nazar solgin, qara samodan,
Bu tok novdasini qo‘riqlagin.
O‘ng qo‘ling o‘tqazgan ildizni,
O‘zing uchun kuchaytirgan shoxchani qo‘riqlagin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 79:15-16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='8' verse='33' id='R8v33'>
<text>Xudoning tanlaganlarini kim ayblay olardi? !
Xudoning O‘zi ularni oqlaydi–ku!</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 8:33</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-25'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 25 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='118' verse='18' id='Ps118v18'>
<text>Egam meni qattiq jazoladi,
Lekin o‘lishimga yo‘l qo‘ymadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 117:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='26' chapter='18' verse='23' id='Ez18v23'>
<text>Nahotki Men fosiq odamning o‘limini istasam?
Yo‘q! Men uning yomon yo‘ldan qaytishini
va yashashini istayman! –
deb aytmoqda Egamiz Rabbiy.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 18:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-26'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 26 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='145' verse='15' id='Ps145v15'>
<text>Ey Egam,
hammaning ko‘zi umid bilan Senga tikilar,
O‘z paytida ularning rizqini berasan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 144:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='12' verse='6' id='L12v6'>
<text>Beshta chumchuq ikki tangaga sotiladi, shunday emasmi?
Biroq bularning birontasi ham Xudoning nazaridan
chetda qolmagan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 12:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-27'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 27 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='18' chapter='28' verse='24' id='Job28v24'>
<text>Xudo yerning to‘rt tomonini ham ko‘rib turadi,
Falak ostidagi hamma narsani kuzatib turadi.</text>
<ref>Ayub 28:24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='4' verse='22' id='Mc4v22'>
<text>Yashirin har qanday narsa oshkora bo‘ladi,
sirli bo‘lgan har qanday narsa ochiladi.</text>
<ref>Mark 4:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-28'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 28 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='19' verse='11' id='1Rg19v11'>
<text>Egamiz o‘tganda,
qudratli bo‘ron tog‘larni yorib,
qoyalarni parcha–parcha qilib tashladi,
lekin Egamiz bo‘ron ichida emasdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 19:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='17' verse='20' id='L17v20-21'>
<text>Ba’zi farziylar Isodan:
Xudoning Shohligi qachon keladi?
— deb so‘radilar.
Iso ularga shunday javob berdi:
Xudoning Shohligi ko‘zga ko‘rinadigan shaklda kelmaydi.
Hech kim: Qara, Xudoning Shohligi bu yerda,
yoki Ana u yerda, — deb aytmaydi.
Chunki Xudoning Shohligi sizlarning orangizdadir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 17:20-21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-29'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 29 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='15' chapter='7' verse='28' id='Esr7v28'>
<text>Egam Xudo menga yor bo‘lgani uchun,
men dadil bo‘ldim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ezra 7:28</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='51' verse='16' id='Is51v16'>
<text>Og‘zingizga so‘zlarimni soldim,
Sizlarni qo‘lim soyasida yashirdim.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 51:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-30'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 30 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='18' chapter='1' verse='21' id='Job1v21'>
<text>Hamma narsamni Xudo bergan edi,
Xudoning O‘zi olib qo‘ydi.
Egamning nomiga hamdu sanolar bo‘lsin!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ayub 1:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='1' verse='16' id='J1v16'>
<text>Uning cheksiz inoyati tufayli
Biz hammamiz baraka ustiga baraka oldik.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 1:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-08-31'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 31 Avgust 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='87' verse='7' id='Ps87v7'>
<text>Hayotim manbayi Sendadir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 86:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='4' verse='14' id='J4v14'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>Men beradigan suvdan kim ichsa,
abadiy chanqamaydi.
Men beradigan suv o‘sha odamning vujudida
buloqqa aylanib,
abadiy hayot sari jo‘shib oqadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 4:14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-01'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 1 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='15' verse='20' id='Jr15v20'>
<text>O‘zim sen bilan birga bo‘laman,
Seni xalos qilib, qutqaraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 15:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='5' verse='19' id='Act5v19-20'>
<text>Tunda Egamizning bir farishtasi qamoqxona
eshigini ochdi,
havoriylarni tashqariga olib chiqib, dedi:
Boringlar, Ma’badda turib, bu yangi hayot
to‘g‘risidagi xabarni odamlarga aytinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 5:19-20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-02'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 2 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='43' verse='1' id='Is43v1'>
<text>Endi ey Yoqub nasli,
seni yaratgan Egamiz gapirmoqda!
Ey Isroil xalqi,
seni barpo qilgan Egamiz shunday aytmoqda:
Men seni qutqardim,
Sening ismingni aytib chaqirdim,
Sen Menikisan, qo‘rqma!</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 43:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='22' verse='16' id='Act22v16'>
<text>Endi nimani kutyapsan? O‘rningdan tur, suvga cho‘mgin.
Rabbimizga iltijo qilib, gunohlaringni yuvgin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 22:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-03'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 3 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='37' verse='5' id='Ez37v5'>
<text>Egam Rabbiy quruq suyaklarga demoqda:
Men ichingizga ruh solaman,
sizlar tirilasizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 37:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='27' chapter='12' verse='2' id='Dn12v2'>
<text>Qora yer bag‘rida yotganlarning ko‘pchiligi uyg‘onadi:
kimdir abadiy hayotga erishadi,
kimdir sharmandaligu abadiy isnodga
duchor bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Doniyor 12:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-04'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 4 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='27' chapter='2' verse='20' id='Dn2v20'>
<text>Xudoyimiz dono va qudratlidir,
Asrlar osha Uning nomi ulug‘lansin!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Doniyor 2:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='147' verse='5' id='Ps147v5'>
<text>Rabbimiz buyukdir, quvvati ko‘pdir,
Uning donoligi cheksizdir.</text>
<ref>Zabur 146:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-05'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 5 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='1' verse='11' id='J1v11'>
<text>U O‘z yurtiga keldi,
Lekin O‘z xalqi Uni qabul qilmadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 1:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='19' id='J3v19'>
<text>Hukm shunday dalilga asoslangan:
dunyoga nur keldi,
ammo odamlar nurdan ko‘ra
zulmatni yaxshi ko‘rdilar,
chunki ularning qilmishlari yovuz edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 3:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-06'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 6 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='16' chapter='4' verse='9' id='Neh4v9'>
<text>Dushmanlarimizning bizga qarshi o‘ylagan
fitnalaridan xabardor ekanimizni
ularning o‘zlari ham eshitishdi.
Ularning niyatini Xudo puchga chiqargan edi.
Shunday qilib, hammamiz yana devorni ta’mirlash
ishlariga qaytdik.
Har kim o‘z ishiga bordi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Nehemiya 4:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='60' verse='18' id='Is60v18'>
<text>Yurtingda endi zo‘ravonlik tovushi
shitilmaydi,
Chegarang ichida vayronagarchilik,
halokat bo‘lmaydi.
Devorlaringga, Najot, deya nom qo‘yasan,
Darvozalaringga, Sharaf, deya nom berasan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 60:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-07'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 7 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='36' verse='27' id='Ez36v27'>
<text>Ichingizga O‘z Ruhimni solaman.
Sizlar farmonlarimga rioya qiladigan,
qonun–qoidalarimni bitta qoldirmay
bajaradigan bo‘lasizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 36:27</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='5' id='J3v5'>
<intro>Iso Masih Nikodim ismli din arbobiga dedi:</intro>
<text>Cuvdan va Ruhdan tug‘ilmagan bironta odam
Xudoning Shohligiga kirolmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 3:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-08'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 8 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='38' chapter='8' verse='16' id='Zch8v16'>
<text>Quyidagi aytganlarimni qilishingiz kerak:
Bir–biringizga haqiqatni gapiring.
Hukm qilganingizda odil qaror chiqarib,
tinchlik o‘rnating.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Zakariyo 8:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='4' verse='2' id='2T4v2'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus Timofeyga yozgan:</intro>
<text>Xudo kalomini va’z qil,
hozir buning vaqtimi, vaqti emasmi,
demay, doim gapirishga tayyor bo‘l.
Butun sabr-toqat bilan ta’lim berib,
odamlarni mulzam qil,
ularga ta’nayu nasihat qil.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 4:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-09'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 9 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='8' verse='10' id='Jr8v10'>
<text>Ularning kichigidan tortib kattasigacha
Nafsini tiyolmay harom yo‘l bilan pul topishadi.
Payg‘ambaridan tortib ruhoniysigacha —
Hammasi tovlamachilik qilishadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 8:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='24' id='Mt6v24'>
<text>Hech kim ikki xo‘jayinga xizmat qilolmaydi.
U yo birini yomon ko‘rib,
boshqasini yaxshi ko‘radi,
yoki biriga bag‘ishlanib, boshqasini mensimaydi.
Sizlar ham Xudoga, ham boylikka
birdek xizmat qila olmaysizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-10'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 10 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='13' verse='8' id='Gn13v8'>
<text>Shunda Ibrom Lutga dedi:
— Mening cho‘ponlarim bilan sening
cho‘ponlaring o‘rtasida janjal bo‘lmasligi kerak.
Axir, biz yaqin qarindoshlarmiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 13:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='59' chapter='3' verse='18' id='Jc3v18'>
<text>Tinchlik o‘rnatuvchilar tinchlikni ekib,
solihlikni o‘rib oladilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yoqub 3:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-11'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 11 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='20' verse='25' id='L20v25'>
<text>Qaysarning haqini Qaysarga,
Xudoning haqini Xudoga beringlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 20:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='8' verse='20' id='Act8v20-21'>
<text>Butrus Shimo‘nga shunday javob berdi:
— Puling o‘zing bilan birga do‘zaxga ravona bo‘lsin,
chunki sen, Xudoning in’omini pulga sotib
olsam bo‘ladi, deb o‘ylaysan.
Bu ishda sening na ulushing, na haqing bor!
Sening yuraging Xudo nazarida to‘g‘ri emas.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 8:20-21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-12'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 12 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='115' verse='2' id='Ps115v2-3'>
<text>Nima uchun begona xalqlar:
“Qani ularning Xudosi”, deya aytarlar?
Bizning Xudoyimiz samolardadir,
U istaganini qilaveradi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 113:10-11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='61' chapter='3' verse='3' id='2P3v3-4'>
<text>Oxirgi kunlarda shunday mazaxchilar bo‘ladiki,
ular chirkin ehtiroslariga berilib yashaydilar.
Sizlarni mazax qilib, shunday deydilar:
“Rabbimiz Iso kelaman deb, so‘z bergan edi. Qani U?!
Mana, ota–bobolarimiz dunyodan o‘tib ketganlaridan beri,
hech narsa o‘zgarmadi. Dunyo bino bo‘lganidan beri,
hamma narsa shundayligicha turibdi.”</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Butrus 3:3-4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-13'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 13 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='18' verse='32' id='Ez18v32'>
<text>Yomon yo‘ldan qayting, yashang! –
deb aytmoqda Egamiz Rabbiy.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 18:32</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='61' chapter='3' verse='9' id='2P3v9'>
<text>Ba’zilar Rabbimiz kelmayapti,
bergan va’dasini bajarishga U kechikyapti, deb o‘ylamoqda.
Aslida unday emas, U sabr–toqat qilyapti,
chunki hech kimning halok bo‘lishini istamay,
hammaning tavba qilishini xohlayapti.</text>
<ref>2 Butrus 3:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-14'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 14 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='54' verse='10' id='Is54v10'>
<text>Tog‘lar o‘rnidan qo‘zg‘alsa ham,
Tepaliklar tebransa ham,
Mening sodiq sevgim sendan ketmaydi,
Mening tinchlik ahdim o‘zgarmaydi,
— demoqda seni sevguvchi — Egamiz.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 54:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='4' verse='22' id='2T4v22'>
<text>Rabbimiz Iso Masih sening ruhingga yor bo‘lsin.
Uning inoyati hammangizga yor bo‘lsin. Omin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 4:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-15'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 15 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='27' id='J6v27'>
<text>Siz o‘tkinchi ozuqa uchun emas,
abadiy hayotga boshlovchi boqiy ozuqa uchun harakat qilinglar.
Bunday ozuqani sizlarga Inson O‘g‘li beradi.
Zotan, Otamiz Xudoning O‘zi bu vazifa uchun Uni ma’qul deb topdi.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 6:27</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='61' chapter='3' verse='11' id='2P3v11'>
<text>Qiyomat kuni butun borliq yonib,
yo‘q bo‘lib ketar ekan,
sizlar Xudoni mamnun qilishga jon kuydiringlar!
Muqaddas hayot kechirishga jon–jahdingiz
bilan harakat qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Butrus 3:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-16'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 16 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='2' verse='2' id='Gn2v2'>
<text>Yettinchi kuni Xudo hamma ishlarini bitirib,
dam oldi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 2:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='4' verse='10' id='H4v10'>
<text>Xudoning farog‘at diyoriga kirganlar
Xudo kabi o‘z ishlaridan dam oladilar,
chunki Xudo ham dunyoni yaratib bo‘lgandan keyin dam olgan edi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 4:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-17'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 17 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='5' verse='5' id='L5v5'>
<text>Shimo‘n Isoga shunday dedi:
— Ustoz, biz tun bo‘yi astoydil harakat qildik,
lekin hech narsa tutolmadik.
Ammo Siz aytganingiz uchun,
to‘r tashlaymiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 5:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='5' verse='29' id='Act5v29'>
<text>Butrus bilan havoriylar shunday javob berdilar:
— Biz insonga emas, Xudoga itoat etishimiz lozim.</text>
<ref>Havoriylar 5:29</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-18'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 18 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='142' verse='8' id='Ps142v8'>
<text>Meni tutqunlikdan chiqarib olgin,
Toki Senga shukrona aytay.
Menga ezgulik qilganing uchun
Solihlar atrofimni o‘rab oladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 141:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='51' chapter='3' verse='16' id='Kol3v16'>
<text>Masihning kalomi sizda chuqur o‘rnashib, yashnayversin.
Donolik bilan bir-biringizga ta’lim bering, nasihat qiling.
Zaburni xonish qilib, madhiyalar va ruhiy qo‘shiqlar bilan,
chin ko‘ngildan minnatdorchilik bildirib, Xudoni tarannum etinglar.</text>
<ref>Kolosaliklar 3:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-19'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 19 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='9' chapter='2' verse='7' id='1Sm2v7-8'>
<text>U kimnidir yo‘qsil, kimnidir boy qilar,
Kimnidir yerga urar, kimnidir yuksaltirar.
Bechorahollarni U tuproqdan ko‘tarar,
Faqirlarni axlatdan olib chiqib yuksaltirar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 2:7-8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='75' verse='8' id='Ps75v8'>
<text>Hukm qiladigan Xudodir,
Birovni U yiqitar, boshqasini yuksaltirar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 74:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-20'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 20 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='29' verse='19' id='Is29v19'>
<text>Bechoralarga Egam yangi quvonch ato etadi,
Isroil xalqining muqaddas Xudosi tufayli
Muhtojlar shod bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 29:19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='6' verse='20' id='L6v20'>
<text>Iso shogirdlariga qarab, dedi:
Ey kambag‘allar, sizlar baxtlisiz!
Xudoning Shohligi sizlarnikidir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 6:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-21'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 21 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='18' id='J14v18'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Men sizlarni yetim qoldirmayman,
yana oldingizga qaytib kelaman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 14:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='3' chapter='26' verse='12' id='Lv26v12'>
<text>Doimo orangizda bo‘laman.
Men sizning Xudoyingiz,
sizlar esa Mening xalqim bo‘lasizlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Levi 26:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-22'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 22 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='58' chapter='13' verse='20' id='H13v20-21'>
<text>Tinchlik beradigan Xudo
bizning Rabbimiz Isoni o‘likdan tiriltirdi.
Iso O‘z qoni bilan abadiy ahdni muhrlagani uchun
Xudo Uni xalqining ulug‘ Cho‘poni qilib tayinladi.
Shu qadar buyuk ishlarni qilgan Xudoning
xohish–irodasini bajara olishingiz uchun
U sizlarga har qanday ezgu fazilatu in’om bersin.
U O‘zining manzur murod–maqsadini
Iso Masih orqali sizlarda bajo keltirsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 13:20-21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='6' verse='13' id='R6v13'>
<text>Tanangizning hech bir a’zosini yomonlik quroli qilib,
gunohning izmiga topshirmanglar.
Aksincha, o‘zingizni Xudoning izmiga topshiringlar,
chunki sizlar oldin o‘lik edingizlar,
endi esa yangi hayotga egasizlar.
Sizlarning tanangiz Xudoning
solihlik quroli bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 6:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-23'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 23 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='2' verse='21' id='Jr2v21'>
<text>Men seni a’lo tokday ekkan edim,
Sen eng sara urug‘dan paydo bo‘lgan eding.
Nechun endi aynib qolding?
Nega yovvoyi tokka aylanib qolding?</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 2:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='3' verse='12' id='H3v12'>
<text>Ey birodarlarim, ehtiyot bo‘linglar!
Yomon niyatga qalbingizdan o‘rin bermanglar,
Xudoga bo‘lgan ishonchingizni yo‘qotmanglar.
Aks holda bu illatlar sizlarni barhayot
Xudodan qaytaradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 3:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-24'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 24 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='7' verse='18' id='J7v18'>
<text>Kim o‘z nomidan gapirsa,
o‘ziga shuhrat izlaydi.
Kim uni yuborganga shuhrat izlasa,
haqiqatni so‘zlaydi,
uning dilida hiyla bo‘lmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 7:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='3' verse='8' id='Ap3v8'>
<text>Sening ishlaringni bilaman.
Mana, oldingda bir eshik ochdim,
uni hech kim bekita olmaydi.
Kuching kamligini Men bilaman.
Shunga qaramay, sen so‘zimga rioya qilding,
Mendan tonmading.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 3:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-25'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 25 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='7' chapter='10' verse='15' id='Jdc10v15'>
<text>Biz gunoh qildik!
Bizga xohlaganingni qil,
ammo bugun bizni dushmanlarimizdan
qutqargin, — deya o‘tindi Isroil xalqi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hakamlar 10:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='18' verse='13' id='L18v13'>
<text>Soliqchi uzoqda turib,
hatto osmonga ham qarashga botinolmay,
ko‘kragiga urganicha:
— Yo Xudo, men gunohkorga rahm qil!
— deb iltijo qilardi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 18:13</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-26'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 26 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='130' verse='3' id='Ps130v3'>
<text>Ey Egam, gunohlarni hisobga olsang agar,
Ey Rabbiy, kim ham bardosh bera olar?!</text>
<ref>Zabur 129:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='23' verse='34' id='L23v34'>
<text>Iso: Ey Ota! Ularni kechirgin,
ular nima qilayotganini bilmaydilar,
— dedi.</text>
<ref>Luqo 23:34</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-27'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 27 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='18' verse='13' id='Mt18v13'>
<text>Cho‘pon adashgan qo‘yni topib olsa,
adashmagan to‘qson to‘qqiztasidan ko‘ra,
shu bitta qo‘y uchun u ko‘proq sevinadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 18:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='15' verse='7' id='L15v7'>
<text>Tavbaga hojat sezmagan to‘qson to‘qqizta
solih odamdan ko‘ra,
tavba qilgan bitta gunohkor uchun
osmonda ko‘proq shodlik bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 15:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-28'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 28 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='27' verse='5' id='Jr27v5'>
<text>Bu dunyoni, yer yuzidagi odamzodu hayvonlarni
Men O‘z qudratim va ajoyibotlarim bilan yaratganman.
Shunday ekan, ularni xohlagan odamga beraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 27:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='1' verse='32' id='L1v32'>
<intro>Farishta Buvi Maryamga o'z o'g'li haqida dedi:</intro>
<text>U buyuk bo‘ladi.
Uni Xudoyi Taoloning O‘g‘li deb atashadi.
Egamiz Xudo Unga bobosi Dovudning taxtini beradi.</text>
<ref>Luqo 1:32</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-29'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 29 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='32' verse='46' id='Dt32v46-47'>
<text>Muso Isroil xalqiga dedi:
Bugun men sizlarni ogohlantirib aytgan
so‘zlarning hammasini yuragingizda saqlang.
Bolalaringizga ham buyuring, mana shu
qonunning so‘zlarini bitta qoldirmay bajarishsin.
Bu shunchaki quruq so‘zlar emas,
balki sizlarning hayotingizdir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 32:46-47</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='55' verse='3' id='Is55v3'>
<text>Quloq soling, menga keling,
Tinglang, shunda yashaysiz.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 55:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-30'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 30 Sentabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='10' id='J14v10'>
<intro>Iso Masih Filipga aytdi:</intro>
<text>Men Otada, Ota esa Menda ekanligiga nahotki ishonmasang? !
Men sizlarga aytgan so‘zlarni O‘zimdan to‘qib gapirmayapman.
Aksincha, Menda yashagan Otam Men orqali O‘z ishlarini bajarmoqda.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 14:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='61' chapter='1' verse='21' id='2P1v21'>
<text>Hech bir haqiqiy payg‘ambar o‘zining
insoniy xohishi bilan bashorat qilgan emas.
Bu payg‘ambarlar Muqaddas Ruh tomonidan boshqarilib,
Xudoning so‘zlarini gapirganlar.</text>
<ref>2 Butrus 1:21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-01'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 1 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='9' chapter='26' verse='23' id='1Sm26v23_2'>
<intro>Dovud alayhissalom shoh Shoulga dedi:</intro>
<text>Bugun Egamiz sizni qo‘limga bergan bo‘lsa–da,
men Egamizning moy surtib tanlaganiga
qo‘l ko‘tarishni istamadim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 26:23</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='51' verse='16' id='Ps51v16'>
<text>Qon to‘kkanim uchun kechir meni, ey Xudo,
Najot berganingni sevinch ila kuylar tilim,
Ey najotkorim Xudo!</text>
<ref>Zabur 50:16</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-02'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 2 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='4' verse='24' id='Mt4v24'>
<text>Iso haqidagi xabar butun Suriyaga yoyildi.
Turli–tuman dardu illatlardan qiynalib yurganlarni,
jinga chalinganlarni, tutqanoq va shol kasaliga yo‘liqqanlarning
hammasini Isoning oldiga keltirishardi.
Iso ularning hammasiga shifo berardi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 4:24</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='24' chapter='3' verse='22' id='Jr3v22'>
<text>Ey, sadoqatsiz farzandlarim,
orqaga qaytinglar!
Bevafo qalbingizga Men shifo beraman.
Sizlar shunday deysizlar:
Mana, oldingga qaytyapmiz,
Axir, Egamiz Xudo Sensan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 3:22</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-03'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 3 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='62' chapter='2' verse='10' id='1J2v10'>
<text>Birodarini sevgan odam nurda yashaydi
va hech qanday narsa uning qulashiga
sabab bo‘la olmaydi.</text>
<ref>1 Yuhanno 2:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='16' verse='14' id='1K16v14'>
<text>Hamma ishlaringizni mehr-muhabbat bilan
bajo keltiringlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 16:14</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-04'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 4 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='25' verse='15' id='Ps25v15'>
<text>Nigohim doimo Egam tomondadir,
U oyoqlarimni tuzoqdan xalos qiladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 24:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='4' verse='18' id='2T4v18'>
<text>Rabbim meni har qanday yomon ishlardan xalos qiladi
va O‘zining samoviy Podshohligiga sog‘-salomat kirgizadi.
Unga abadulabad shon-sharaflar bo‘lsin!
Omin.</text>
<ref>2 Timo‘tiy 4:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-05'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 5 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='146' verse='8' id='Ps146v8_l'>
<text>Egamiz solihlarni sevadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 145:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='23' chapter='50' verse='8' id='Is50v8'>
<text>Meni oqlaydigan yaqinimdadir,
Men bilan da’volashadigan kim?!</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 50:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-06'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 6 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='34' verse='9' id='Ps34v9'>
<text>Egamizning muruvvatini tatib ko‘r,
Egamiz yaxshidir, bilib ol.
Naqadar baxtlidir Unda panoh topganlar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 33:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='55' id='J6v55'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Mening tanam — haqiqiy ozuqa,
qonim haqiqiy ichimlikdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 6:55</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-07'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 7 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='60' verse='2' id='Is60v2'>
<text>Mana, yer yuzini zulmat qopladi,
Xalqlarni quyuq zulmat bosdi.
Ammo Egamiz senga keladi,
Sen uzra Uning ulug‘vorligi porlaydi.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 60:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='10' verse='23' id='H10v23'>
<text>Endi e’tirof etgan umidimizni
ikkilanmay mahkam tutaylik.
Chunki va’da bergan Xudo O‘z so‘ziga sodiqdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 10:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-08'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 8 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='8' verse='20' id='Mt8v20'>
<text>Iso Tavrot tafsirchisiga shunday dedi:
Tulkilarning uyalari bor, qushlarning inlari bor.
Inson O‘g‘lining esa bosh qo‘yadigan joyi yo‘q.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 8:20</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='9' verse='23' id='L9v23'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Kimda–kim Menga ergashishni istasa,
o‘zidan kechsin va har kuni o‘z xochini ko‘tarib,
ortimdan yursin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 9:23</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-09'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 9 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='24' verse='40' id='Gn24v40'>
<intro>Ibrohim payg‘ambar qulboshisiga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men Egam ko‘rsatgan yo‘ldan yuraman,
U O‘zining farishtasini
sen bilan birga jo‘natadi
va seni omadga erishtiradi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 24:40</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='59' chapter='4' verse='15' id='Jc4v15'>
<text>Sizlar: “Egamiz xohish bildirsa,
sog‘–salomat bo‘lsak,
uni yoki buni qilamiz”,
— deb aytishingiz kerak.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yoqub 4:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-10'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 10 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='4' chapter='11' verse='29' id='Nu11v29'>
<text>Muso unga xizmat qilib kelgan Yoshuaga:
Egamning butun xalqi payg‘ambar bo‘lsin,
Egamiz O‘z Ruhini ularning hammasiga bersin,
deyman!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Sahroda 11:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='16' id='J14v16-17'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>Men Otaga murojaat qilaman
va U sizlar bilan to abad qoladigan
boshqa Homiyni yuboradi.
Bu Homiy — Haqiqat Ruhidir.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 14:16-17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-11'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 11 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='8' verse='52' id='1Rg8v52'>
<text>Xalqing Senga doimo iltijo qilganda,
men, qulingning iltijolarini,
xalqing iltijolarini eshitib,
ularga doimo nazaringni solib marhamat qilgin.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 8:52</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='118' verse='25' id='Ps118v25'>
<text>Najot ber bizga, yolvoramiz, ey Egam!
Yolvoramiz, omad ber bizga, ey Egam!</text>
<ref>Zabur 117:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-12'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 12 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='14' chapter='16' verse='9' id='2Chr16v9'>
<text>Egamiz yer yuzidagi hammani kuzatib turadi,
Unga sodiq bo‘lganlarga
U kuch–qudrat beradi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Solnomalar 16:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='2' id='Ps119v2'>
<text>Baxtlidir Sening shartlaringga rioya qiladiganlar,
Butun qalbi bilan Senga intiladiganlar.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-13'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 13 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='21' verse='14' id='L21v14'>
<text>O‘zimizni qanday himoya qilamiz,
deb oldindan qayg‘urmaslikka qaror
qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 21:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='4' verse='29' id='Act4v29'>
<text>Ey Egamiz, ularning tahdidlariga qara!
Bu qullaring jasorat bilan
Sening so‘zingni aytishlari uchun bizga imkon ber.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 4:29</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-14'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 14 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='32' verse='39' id='Dt32v39_I'>
<text>O‘ldiradigan Menman,
Hayot beradigan ham Menman,
Jarohat yetkazadigan Menman,
Shifo beradigan ham Menman.
Mening qo‘limdan hech kim qutula olmaydi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 32:39</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='12' verse='4' id='L12v4'>
<text>Sizlarga shuni aytay, do‘stlarim,
tanani o‘ldirib, undan keyin boshqa biron
narsa qila olmaydiganlardan qo‘rqmanglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 12:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-15'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 15 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='16' verse='21' id='Mt16v21'>
<text>Iso shogirdlariga quyidagilarni ochiqchasiga
tushuntira boshladi:
Men Quddusga borib, oqsoqollar, bosh ruhoniylar
va Tavrot tafsirchilari qo‘lida ko‘p azob chekaman.
Meni o‘ldirishadi, lekin uchinchi kuni Men tirilaman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 16:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='13' verse='33' id='L13v33'>
<intro>Iso Masih ulamolarga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men bugun, ertaga va indinga O‘z yo‘limdan qolmasligim kerak.
Axir, payg‘ambar Quddusdan tashqarida o‘ldirilishi mumkin emas.</text>
<ref>Luqo 13:33</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-16'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 16 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='54' chapter='2' verse='5' id='1T2v5-6'>
<text>Xudo yagona va Xudo bilan insonlar
orasidagi Vositachi ham yagonadir.
O‘zi ham inson bo‘lgan Iso Masih
hamma insonlarni qutqarish evaziga
O‘z jonini fido qildi.</text>
<ref>1 Timo‘tiy 2:5-6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='48' chapter='1' verse='4' id='G1v4'>
<text>Iso Masih bizni hozirgi yovuz zamondan qutqaray,
deb bizning gunohlarimiz uchun O‘zini fido qildi.
U shu yo‘sin Otamiz Xudoning irodasini ado etdi.</text>
<ref>Galatiyaliklar 1:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-17'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 17 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='16' verse='23' id='J16v23'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Mening nomimdan Otadan nima so‘rasangizlar,
U sizlarga beradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 16:23</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='22' verse='17' id='Ap22v17'>
<text>Kim chanqagan bo‘lsa, kelsin.
Kim xohlasa,
hayotbaxsh suvdan tekin bahra olsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 22:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-18'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 18 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='37' id='J6v37'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>Otam Menga bergan har bir odam
Mening oldimga keladi.
Oldimga kelgan bironta odamni
Men aslo haydab yubormayman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 6:37</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='10' verse='48' id='Mc10v48-49'>
<text>Ko‘p odamlar Bartimeyga:
“Jim bo‘l!” deb jerkishdi. Lekin u:
— Ey Dovud O‘g‘li, menga rahm qil!
— deb yanada qattiqroq baqirdi.
Iso to‘xtab: “Uni chaqirib kelinglar”, dedi.
Odamlar kelib, ko‘r odamga:
“Dadil bo‘l, o‘rningdan tur.
U seni chaqiryapti”, deb aytishdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 10:48-49</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-19'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 19 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='22' verse='29' id='L22v29'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Shuning uchun,
Otam Menga in’om qilgan Shohlikni
Men sizlarga in’om qilyapman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 22:29</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='18' verse='36' id='J18v36'>
<text>Iso hokim Pilatga javoban:
— Mening Shohligim bu dunyodan emas.
Agar Shohligim bu dunyodan bo‘lganda edi,
yahudiylarning qo‘liga tushmasligim
uchun Mening xizmatkorlarim kurashar edilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 18:36</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-20'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 20 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='25' verse='18' id='Ps25v18'>
<text>Kulfatu g‘amlarimni ko‘rib,
Barcha gunohlarimdan o‘tgin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 24:18</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='1' verse='9' id='1J1v9'>
<text>Gunohlarimizni e’tirof etsak,
sodiq va adolatli bo‘lgan Xudo gunohlarimizni kechirib,
bizni har qanday yomonlikdan forig‘ qiladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 1:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-21'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 21 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='19' verse='5' id='L19v5-6'>
<text>Iso Zakkayga dedi:
Zakkay! Tezroq pastga tush,
Men bugun sening uyingda mehmon
bo‘lishim kerak.
Zakkay darrov pastga tushdi,
Isoni quvonch bilan uyiga taklif qildi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 19:5-6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='7' id='J3v7'>
<text>Sizlar qaytadan tug‘ilishingiz kerak,
deganimga taajjublanmang.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 3:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-22'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 22 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='16' verse='6' id='Ps16v6'>
<text>Chegara chiziqlari tushgan
Men uchun huzurbaxsh joylarga,
Naqadar ajoyib mulkim bor!</text>
<ref>Zabur 15:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='1' verse='11' id='E1v11'>
<text>Biz Masih orqali Xudoning xalqi bo‘ldik.
Bu Xudoning azaldan belgilagan rejasi
bo‘yicha amalga oshdi.
Axir, Xudo har bir narsani O‘z xohish–irodasi
bo‘yicha amalga oshiradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 1:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-23'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 23 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='23' verse='8' id='Ex23v8'>
<text>Pora olmanglar.
Pora tufayli ko‘zi ochiqlarning
ko‘zini yog‘ bosadi.
Pora har doim to‘g‘ri odamlarning
ishiga zarar yetkazadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 23:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='54' chapter='6' verse='10' id='1T6v10'>
<text>Har turli yomonlikning tomiri pulparastlikdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Timo‘tiy 6:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-24'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 24 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='5' verse='2' id='Ps5v2-3'>
<text>So‘zlarimga quloq tut, ey Egam!
Diqqat qilgin nolalarimga.
Eshitgin, madad so‘rab iltijo etaman,
Sen ham Shohimsan, ham Xudoyimsan!
Shu bois Senga ibodat qilaman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 5:2-3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='16' verse='20' id='J16v20'>
<intro>Iso Masih shogirdlariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Sizlar yig‘lab dod–faryod qilasizlar,
dunyo esa quvonadi. Sizlar qayg‘urasiz,
lekin qayg‘ungiz shodlikka aylanadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 16:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-25'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 25 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='3' verse='3' id='Ps3v3-4'>
<text>Ko‘plar men haqimda:
“Xudodan unga najot yo‘q”, — deb aytadilar.
Ey Egam, Mening qalqonimsan!
Shuhratim Sensan!
Sen boshimni yuksaltirasan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 3:3-4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='5' verse='2' id='R5v2'>
<text>Rabbimiz Iso Xudoning inoyati eshigini
bizga ochib berdi.
Biz imon tufayli bu inoyatga erishib,
mahkam turamiz hamda Xudoning ulug‘vorligiga
sherik bo‘lish umidimiz borligidan faxrlanamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 5:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-26'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 26 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='32' verse='10' id='Ps32v10'>
<text>Fosiqning azobi ko‘pdir,
Lekin Egamizdan umidvorlarni
Sodiq sevgi qurshab oladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 31:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='39' chapter='3' verse='18' id='Ml3v18'>
<text>Sizlar solihu fosiqning farqini yana ko‘rasiz.
Ha, Menga xizmat qiladiganu Menga
xizmat qilmaydiganning holini bilasiz.</text>
<ref>Mal’axi 3:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-27'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 27 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='6' verse='48' id='J6v48'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Men hayot noniman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 6:48</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='105' verse='40' id='Ps105v40-42'>
<text>Isroil go‘sht so‘raganda Egamiz bedanalar berdi,
Osmondan non yog‘dirib, ularni to‘yg‘azdi.
Egamiz qoyani ochdi, suv otilib chiqdi,
Sahro bo‘ylab daryoday suv oqdi.
Egamiz O‘zining muqaddas va’dasini,
O‘z quli Ibrohimga bergan va’dasini yodda tutdi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 104:40-42</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-28'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 28 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='53' chapter='1' verse='2' id='2Th1v2'>
<text>Otamiz Xudo va Rabbimiz Iso Masihning
inoyati, tinchligi sizlarga yor bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Salonikaliklar 1:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='4' chapter='6' verse='26' id='Nu6v26'>
<text>Egam nazarini senga solsin,
Senga tinchlik ato etsin!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Cho‘lda 6:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-29'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 29 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='35' chapter='1' verse='2' id='Hab1v2'>
<text>Ey Egam,
qachongacha Sendan yordam so‘rab yolvoray? !
Menga quloq solasanmi o‘zi?!
Qachongacha: “Zo‘ravonlikdan qutqar!”
— deb iltijo qilay?!
Bizga najot berasanmi o‘zi?!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Habaqquq 1:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='130' verse='1' id='Ps130v1-2'>
<text>Ey Egam, tubsiz suvlardan Senga nola qilaman.
Ey Rabbiy, mening ovozimni eshitgin!
Iltijolarimga diqqat ila quloq solgin!</text>
<ref>Zabur 129:1-2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-30'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 30 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='12' chapter='20' verse='3' id='2Rg20v3'>
<intro>Shoh Hizqiyo qattiq kasal bo‘lib yolvordi:</intro>
<text>“Ey, Egam! Chin qalbimdan Senga sodiq bo‘lib,
yo‘llaringdan yurganimni
va oldingda to‘g‘ri ishlar qilganimni esla.”
Shunday deb achchiq–achchiq yig‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 4 Shohlar 20:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='30' verse='12' id='Ps30v12'>
<text>Azamni Sen to‘yga aylantirding,
Aza libosini egnimdan olib tashlading,
Shodlikni menga kiygizding.</text>
<ref>Zabur 29:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-10-31'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 31 Oktabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='53' verse='11' id='Is53v11_D'>
<text>Mening solih qulim o‘z bilimi tufayli
Ko‘pchilikni oqlab,
ularning aybini o‘ziga oladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 53:11</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='5' verse='17' id='Mt5v17'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Meni, Tavrot yoki payg‘ambarlarning bitiklarini
bekor qilgani kelgan, deb o‘ylamanglar.
Men bekor qilgani emas,
balki bajo keltirgani keldim.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 5:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-01'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 1 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='29' chapter='2' verse='11' id='Joel2v11-12'>
<text>Egamizning kuni chindan dahshatli!
Bu vahimali kunga bardosh bergay kim?!
Egamizning kalomi shudir:
Hozir ham kech emas,
Ro‘za tutib, yig‘lab, qayg‘urib,
Butun qalbingiz bilan Menga qaytinglar.</text>
<ref>Yo‘il 2:11-12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='15' verse='10' id='L15v10'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Tavba qilgan bitta gunohkor uchun
Xudoning farishtalari huzurida
shodlik bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 15:10</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-02'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 2 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='65' verse='8' id='Ps65v8'>
<text>Dengizlar hayqirig‘ini bostirasan,
To‘lqinlar shovqinini tinchitasan.
Xalqlar shovqin–suroniga barham berasan.</text>
<ref>Zabur 64:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='8' verse='26' id='Mt8v26'>
<text>Iso turib, shamolga va to‘lqinlarga do‘q urdi.
Shu ondayoq chuqur sukunat cho‘kdi.</text>
<ref>Matto 8:26</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-03'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 3 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='1' verse='25' id='Gn1v25'>
<text>Xudo har turli yovvoyi hayvonlarni,
chorvaning har xil turlarini,
yer yuzida sudralib yuruvchi jonivorlarning
va hasharotlarning har xil turlarini yaratdi.
Xudo buning ajoyib ekanini ko‘rdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 1:25</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='8' verse='20' id='R8v20-21'>
<text>Mavjudot behudalikka mubtalo bo‘lgan.
Bu mavjudotning ixtiyori bilan emas,
balki Xudoning ixtiyori bilan shunday bo‘ldi.
Shunday bo‘lsa–da,
mavjudot chirib–bitish qulligidan ozod etilib,
Xudoning farzandlari bilan birga
ulug‘vor erkinlikdan bahramand bo‘lishiga umid bor.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 8:20-21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-04'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 4 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='18' chapter='9' verse='4' id='Job9v4'>
<text>Ha, Xudo dono va qudratlidir,
Kim Xudoga qarshi chiqib,
Undan ustun bo‘lgan?!</text>
<ref>Ayub 9:4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='147' verse='3' id='Ps147v3'>
<text>Ezilgan ko‘ngillarga U shifo beradi,
Ularning yaralariga malham qo‘yadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 146:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-05'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 5 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='15' verse='2' id='Ex15v2_D'>
<text>Egam mening Xudoyimdir, men Uni olqishlayman,
Otamning Xudosidir, men Uni ulug‘layman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 15:2</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='20' verse='8' id='Ps20v8'>
<text>Ba’zilar jang aravalariga ishonadi,
Ba’zilar otlari bilan maqtanadi,
Biz esa Egamiz Xudoga ishonamiz.</text>
<ref>Zabur 19:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-06'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 6 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='49' chapter='2' verse='6' id='E2v6'>
<text>Xudo bizni Masih bilan birga tiriltirdi
va bizga samoda U bilan birga joy berdi.
Bular Iso Masih tufayli amalga oshdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 2:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='6' verse='4' id='R6v4'>
<text>Biz suvga cho‘mdirilib,
Masih bilan birga o‘ldik va ko‘mildik.
Otamiz Xudoning ulug‘vor qudrati bilan
Iso Masih o‘likdan tirilganiday,
biz yangi hayotga ega bo‘lamiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 6:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-07'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 7 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='77' id='Ps119v77'>
<text>Menga shafqat qilgin, toki yashayin,
Axir, Sening qonuning men uchun lazzat.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:77</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='26' verse='39' id='Mt26v39'>
<intro>Iso Masih ibodat qildi:</intro>
<text>Ey Otam, agar iloji bo‘lsa,
bu azob kosasi Meni chetlab o‘tsin.
Ammo Mening xohishim emas,
Sening xohishing bajo bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 26:39</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-08'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 8 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='109' verse='31' id='Ps109v31'>
<text>Egamiz turar yo‘qsullarning o‘ng tomonida,
Ularni o‘limga mahkum etganlardan qutqarmoq uchun.</text>
<ref>Zabur 108:31</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='14' chapter='19' verse='6' id='2Chr19v6'>
<text>Shoh Yohushafat hakamlarga shunday ko‘rsatma berdi:
Hukm qilishda ehtiyot bo‘linglar,
chunki sizlar inson nomidan emas,
balki Egamiz nomidan hukm qilasiz.
Hukm qilayotganingizda U sizlar bilan birga bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 2 Solnomalar 19:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-09'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 9 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='3' chapter='22' verse='32' id='Lv22v32'>
<text>Meni — Muqaddas Xudoni badnom qilmang.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Leviy 22:32</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='9' id='Mt6v9'>
<text>Sizlar esa shunday ibodat qilinglar:
Bizning osmondagi Otamiz!
Sening muqaddas noming ulug‘lansin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-10'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 10 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='38' chapter='12' verse='10' id='Zch12v10_A'>
<text>Men Dovud avlodiga, Quddus aholisiga
mehr–shafqat va ibodat ruhini yog‘diraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Zakariyo 12:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='9' verse='4' id='R9v4-5'>
<text>Ular Isroil xalqidir.
Xudo ularni O‘ziga farzand qilib olish uchun tanladi.
O‘zining ulug‘vorligini ularga namoyon qilib,
ular bilan ahdlar tuzdi.
Ularga O‘z qonunini berib,
ularni O‘zining xizmatiga tayinladi
hamda ularga O‘z va’dalarini berdi.
Ular ulug‘ ota–bobolardan kelib chiqqan,
Masih ham jismoniy jihatdan
Isroil xalqidan kelib chiqqan.</text>
<ref>Rimliklar 9:4-5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-11'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 11 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='1' verse='13' id='L1v13'>
<text>Farishta unga dedi:
Zakariyo, qo‘rqma, sening iltijolaring ijobat bo‘ldi.
Xotining Elizabet senga bir o‘g‘il tug‘ib beradi.
Uning ismini Yahyo qo‘yasan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 1:13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='9' chapter='1' verse='27' id='1Sm1v27'>
<intro>Xanna Elaxga:</intro>
<text>Men mana shu bola uchun Egamga
iltijo qilgan edim,
Egam tilagimni bajo qildi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 1 Shohlar 1:27</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-12'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 12 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='6' verse='12' id='1K6v12'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavel yozgan:</intro>
<text>Hamma narsa menga joiz ekan,
lekin hamma narsa ham foydali emas.
Hamma narsa menga joiz ekan,
lekin hech bir narsa menga hokim bo‘lmasligi kerak.</text>
<ref>1 Korinfliklar 6:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='5' verse='10' id='E5v10-11'>
<text>Rabbimizga nima maqbul ekanligini
bilishga tirishinglar.
Zulmatning besamara ishlarida ishtirok etmanglar,
aksincha, ularni fosh etinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 5:10-11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-13'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 13 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='78' verse='3' id='Ps78v3-4'>
<text>Egamizning hamdga loyiq ishlarini,
Uning qudratini, U qilgan ajoyibotlarni
Biz yashirmaymiz ularning bolalaridan,
Hikoya qilarmiz kelgusi avlodlarga ham.</text>
<ref>Zabur 77:3-4</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='14' verse='27' id='Act14v27'>
<text>Havoriylar Antioxiyaga kelganlaridan keyin,
jamoatni bir joyga yig‘dilar va
Xudo ular orqali nimalar qilganini,
g‘ayriyahudiylarning imonga kelishi uchun
Xudo qanday yo‘l ochib berganini
aytib berdilar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 14:27</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-14'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 14 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='55' verse='6' id='Is55v6'>
<text>Egangiz yoningizda ekan, Unga intiling,
U yaqiningizda ekan, Uni chaqiring!</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 55:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='11' verse='9' id='L11v9'>
<text>So‘rang va sizga beriladi.
Izlang, topasizlar.
Taqillating, eshik ochiladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 11:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-15'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 15 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='9' verse='2' id='J9v2-3'>
<text>Shogirdlari Isodan so‘radilar:
— Ustoz, kimning gunohi uning ko‘r bo‘lib tug‘ilishiga sababchi
bo‘ldi? O‘zinikimi yoki ota–onasinikimi?
Iso shunday javob berdi:
— Bu odamning gunohi ham, ota–onasining gunohi ham
bunga sabab bo‘lmagan.
Xudoning ishlari unda namoyon bo‘lishi uchun u ko‘r
tug‘ilgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 9:2-3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='9' verse='2' id='Mt9v2'>
<text>Iso shaharga kirishi bilanoq bir necha
kishi Uning oldiga to‘shakda yotgan bir shol
odamni ko‘tarib keldilar.
Iso ularning ishonchini ko‘rib, sholga:
— Dadil bo‘l, o‘g‘lim, gunohlaring kechirildi, — dedi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 9:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-16'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 16 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='146' verse='8' id='Ps146v8'>
<text>Egamiz ikki bukilganlarning
qaddini rostlaydi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 145:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='3' verse='6' id='Act3v6'>
<text>Butrus dedi:
— Mening pulim yo‘q,
ammo o‘zimda bor narsani senga beraman.
Nosiralik Iso Masih nomi bilan senga buyuraman:
o‘rningdan turib yur!</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 3:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-17'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 17 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='41' chapter='14' verse='38' id='Mc14v38'>
<text>Ko‘z–quloq bo‘lib turinglar,
vasvasaga tushmaslik uchun ibodat qilinglar.
Ruh tetik, tana esa zaifdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 14:38</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='6' verse='18' id='E6v18'>
<text>Har qanday sharoitda Muqaddas Ruhga tayanib
duo–ibodat qilinglar.
Ibodatda hushyor va sabotli bo‘lib,
barcha Xudoning azizlari uchun iltijo qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 6:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-18'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 18 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='1' verse='7' id='Ex1v7'>
<text>Isroil nasli barakali bo‘lib,
borgan sari ko‘payib boraverdi.
Misr yurti ular bilan to‘lib–toshdi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 1:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='3' chapter='26' verse='9' id='Lv26v9'>
<text>Sizlarga yuz buraman, barakali qilib ko‘paytiraman.
Sizlar bilan qilgan ahdimga sodiq qolaman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Leviy 26:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-19'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 19 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='40' verse='26' id='Is40v26'>
<text>Ko‘zlaringizni osmonga tiking, qarang:
Axir, bularni kim yaratgan?
Xudo osmonga yulduzlarni terib qo‘ygan–ku!
Uning O‘zi har biriga nom bergan–ku!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 40:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='1' verse='20' id='R1v20'>
<text>Borliq yaratilgandan beri
Xudoning ko‘rinmas xususiyatlari,
ya’ni abadiy qudrati va ilohiyoti,
ochiq ko‘rinib turibdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 1:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-20'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 20 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='37' chapter='2' verse='8' id='Hgg2v8'>
<text>Sarvari Olamning kalomi shudir:
“Kumush Meniki, oltin ham Menikidir.”</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hagay 2:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='6' verse='20' id='Mt6v20'>
<text>O‘zlaringiz uchun osmonda boylik yig‘inglar.
Bunday boylikni kuya yemaydi,
zang bosmaydi, o‘g‘ri ham o‘g‘irlay olmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 6:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-21'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 21 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='2' verse='35' id='Jr2v35'>
<text>Aybsizman, deb aytasan.
Egamiz g‘azabidan tushgani aniq, deysan.
Gunoh qilmadim, deganing uchun,
Men seni jazolayman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 2:35</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='5' verse='9' id='R5v9'>
<text>Demak, biz Masihning to‘kilgan qoni tufayli
oqlangan ekanmiz, albatta U bizni
Xudoning qahr–g‘azabidan qutqaradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 5:9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-22'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 22 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='77' verse='3' id='Ps77v3'>
<text>Qayg‘uli kunimda Rabbiyga intildim,
Tunda qo‘llarimni ko‘tarib iltijo qildim,
Jonim tasalli topishni rad etdi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 76:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='5' verse='7' id='H5v7'>
<text>Masih bu dunyoda yashagan paytda ko‘z yosh to‘kib,
Xudoga faryod qildi, Unga iltijo qilib yolvordi.
Chunki Xudo Uni o‘limdan qutqarishga
qodir ekanligini Masih bilar edi.
U Xudoni yuksak darajada e’zozlagani
uchun Uning iltijosi ijobat bo‘ldi.</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 5:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-23'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 23 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='15' verse='26' id='Ex15v26'>
<text>Sizlarga shifo beradigan Egangiz Menman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 15:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='2' verse='17' id='Mc2v17'>
<intro>Iso Masih Tavrot tafsirchilariga dedi:</intro>
<text>Men solihlarni emas, gunohkorlarni tavbaga chaqirgani kelganman.
Axir, sog‘lar emas, xastalar tabibga muhtojdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 2:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-24'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 24 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='23' verse='45' id='L23v45'>
<intro>Iso Masih o‘lmasidan avval:</intro>
<text>Tush payti edi. Kun qoraydi,
soat uchga qadar hamma yoq zulmatga cho‘mdi.
Ma’baddagi parda o‘rtasidan yirtildi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 23:44-45</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='9' verse='12' id='H9v12'>
<text>Masih eng muqaddas xonaga kirdi.
U bu xonaga takalar va buqalarning qoni bilan emas,
balki O‘z qoni evaziga kirdi.
U yerga bir marta kirib,
bizni to abad gunohlardan ozod qildi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 9:12</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-25'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 25 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='31' verse='3' id='Gn31v3'>
<text>Egamiz Yoqubga:
— Ota–bobolaringning yurtiga,
qarindosh–urug‘laringning oldiga qayt,
Men sen bilan birga bo‘laman, — dedi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 31:3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='1' chapter='50' verse='24' id='Gn50v24'>
<text>“Mening umrim oxirlab boryapti”, dedi Yusuf aka–ukalariga.
“Lekin Xudo sizlarni kuzatib turadi,
sizlarni bu yurtdan olib chiqib, Ibrohim,
Is’hoq va Yoqubga beraman,
deb qasam ichgan yurtga qaytarib olib boradi.”</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 50:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-26'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 26 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='47' chapter='11' verse='30' id='2K11v30'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Agar maqtanish menga lozim bo‘lsa,
o‘z zaifligim bilan maqtanaman.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Korinfliklar 11:30</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='46' chapter='1' verse='31' id='1K1v31'>
<text>Maqtanaman degan Rabbimiz bilan maqtansin.</text>
<ref>1 Korinfliklar 1:31</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-27'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 27 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='6' verse='22' id='R6v22'>
<text>Endi gunohdan ozod qilinib,
Xudoning quli bo‘lib qoldingiz.
Buning natijasi muqaddaslik va abadiy hayotdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 6:22</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='2' verse='7' id='Ap2v7'>
<text>Kimning qulog‘i bo‘lsa,
Ruhning jamoatlarga aytayotgan gaplarini eshitsin.
G‘olib kelganlarga Xudoning jannatidagi hayot daraxti
mevasidan yeyishni nasib etaman.</text>
<ref>Vahiy 2:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-28'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 28 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='16' verse='16' id='L16v16'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Yahyo va undan oldin kelganlar Tavrot va
payg‘ambarlar bitiklarini e’lon qilganlar.
Endi esa Xudoning Shohligi to‘g‘risidagi Xushxabar
e’lon qilinmoqda va har bir odam
bu Shohlikka kirishga undalmoqda.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 16:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='18' verse='2' id='Mt18v2-3'>
<text>Iso yoniga bir bolani chaqirdi,
uni o‘rtalarida turg‘izib, dedi:
Sizlarga chinini aytayin:
agar sizlar o‘zgarmasangiz va bolalarday bo‘lmasangiz,
hech qachon Osmon Shohligiga kira olmaysizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 18:2-3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-29'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 29 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='43' verse='18' id='Is43v18-19'>
<text>O‘tmishdagilarni yodga olmang,
Qadimgilarni o‘ylayvermang.
Mana, Men yangi bir ish qilyapman.
Shu paytning o‘zidayoq sodir bo‘lyapti!
Ko‘rmayapsizmi?!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 43:18-19</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='2' verse='18' id='L2v18-19'>
<text>Cho‘ponlarning gapini eshitganlarning
hammasi hayratga tushdi.
Maryam esa bu so‘zlarning barini
diliga tugib olib,
chuqur o‘ylab yurdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 2:18-19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-11-30'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 30 Noyabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='33' verse='5' id='Ps33v5'>
<text>Egamiz adolatu haqiqatni sevadi,
Zamin Uning sodiq sevgisiga to‘la.</text>
<ref>Zabur 32:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='2' verse='4' id='R2v4'>
<text>Xudoning cheksiz mehribonligi
va sabr–toqatini pisand qilmayotganingni qara.
Axir, Uning muruvvati seni tavbaga yetaklashini bilmaysanmi?!</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 2:4</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-01'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 1 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='40' chapter='13' verse='37' id='Mt13v37'>
<text>Iso shogirdlariga shunday javob berdi:
— Yaxshi urug‘ sepuvchi Inson O‘g‘lidir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 13:37</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='41' chapter='4' verse='31' id='Mc4v31-32'>
<text>Xudoning Shohligi xantal doniga o‘xshaydi:
u yerga sepiladigan urug‘larning eng maydasidir.
Lekin sepilgandan keyin ko‘karadi
va barcha ko‘katlardan baland bo‘lib o‘sadi.
Katta shoxlar chiqaradi, osmondagi qushlar
ham uning panohida uya quradi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Mark 4:31-32</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-02'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 2 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='12' verse='1' id='Is12v1'>
<text>Senga shukr aytaman, ey Egam,
Mendan g‘azablangan eding,
G‘azabing bosildi, ey Egam,
Menga Sen tasalli berasan!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 12:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='15' verse='26' id='Mt15v26-27'>
<text>Iso kan’onlik ayolga:
— Bolalardan nonni olib kuchuklarga tashlash
yaxshi emas, — dedi.
— To‘g‘ri, Hazrat, — dedi ayol. —
Lekin kuchuklar ham xo‘jayinlarining dasturxonidan
to‘kilgan ushoqlarini yeydi–ku.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 15:26-27</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-03'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 3 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='45' chapter='1' verse='7' id='R1v7'>
<text>Xudo sizlarning hammangizni yaxshi ko‘rib,
O‘zining aziz xalqi bo‘lishga chorlagan.
Otamiz Xudo va Rabbimiz Iso Masih sizlarga
inoyat va tinchlik ato qilsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 1:7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='50' chapter='4' verse='7' id='Ph4v7'>
<text>Xudo beradigan, inson xayoliga sig‘maydigan
tinchlik Iso Masih orqali sizlarning
yuraklaringizni va o‘y–xayollaringizni
qo‘riqlaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Filipiliklar 4:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-04'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 4 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='52' chapter='5' verse='12' id='1Th5v12-13'>
<text>Birodarlar, sizlarga iltijo qilamiz.
Orangizda ishlab, Rabbimiz Isoning yo‘lida
sizlarga yetakchilik qilayotgan,
yo‘l–yo‘riq ko‘rsatayotganlarni hurmat qiling.
Qilayotgan ishlari uchun muhabbat bilan
ularni e’zozlang.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 5:12-13</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='5' chapter='32' verse='7' id='Dt32v7'>
<text>Qadimgi kunlarni eslang,
Uzoq o‘tmishni o‘ylang.
Otalaringizdan so‘rang, u sizlarga aytib beradi,
Oqsoqollardan so‘rang, sizlarga gapirib berishadi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 32:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-05'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 5 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='24' verse='26' id='L24v26'>
<text>Masih ulug‘lanishidan oldin bu azoblarni
boshdan kechirishi kerak edi–ku!</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 24:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='60' chapter='3' verse='18' id='1P3v18'>
<text>Masih bizni gunohlarimizdan
to abad forig‘ qilish uchun
azob chekkanini yodingizda tutinglar.
U solih bo‘la turib,
biz, gunohkorlarni Xudoga yaqinlashtirish uchun
jonini fido qildi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Butrus 3:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-06'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 6 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='119' verse='82' id='Ps119v82'>
<text>Va’dalaringni kutib, ko‘zimning nuri so‘nadi,
“Qachon menga tasalli berasan?”
deya so‘rayman.</text>
<ref>Zabur 118:82</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='42' chapter='11' verse='28' id='L11v28'>
<text>Iso dedi:
Xudoning kalomini tinglab,
unga rioya qiladiganlar baxtlidir!</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 11:28</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-07'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 7 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='16' chapter='8' verse='8' id='Neh8v8'>
<text>Ular Xudoning Tavrot kitobidan o‘qib,
o‘qiganlarini tarjima qilib berardilar,
Tavrotning mazmunini tushuntirardilar,
shuning uchun xalq o‘qilganlarni tushundi.</text>
<ref>Nehemiya 8:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='55' chapter='3' verse='16' id='2T3v16-17'>
<text>Har bir Muqaddas Yozuv ilohiy ilhom bilan yozilgan bo‘lib,
ta’lim berish, dalolat qilish, tuzatish,
solihlik yo‘lida tarbiya berish uchun foydalidir.
Shu yo‘sin Xudoning quli komil
va har qanday yaxshi ishga qobil bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 2 Timo‘tiy 3:16-17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-08'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 8 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='9' verse='10' id='Ps9v10'>
<text>Mazlum uchun Egamiz qal’aday bo‘ladi,
Ha, qayg‘uli damlarda U panoh bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 9:10</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='6' verse='18' id='H6v18'>
<text>Xudo yolg‘on gapirmaydi!
Uning bergan va’dasi va ichgan qasami
hech qachon o‘zgarmaydi.
Xudo tasdiqlagan va’dasidan endi biz kuchli
dalda olib, oldimizga qo‘yilgan umidni
mahkam tutaylik.
Axir, biz Xudodan panoh topganmiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Ibroniylar 6:18</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-09'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 9 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='46' chapter='4' verse='5' id='1K4v5'>
<text>Vaqtidan oldin, Rabbimiz kelmagunlaricha,
aslo hukm yuritmanglar.
U kelib zulmatda yashirilgan narsalarni
ravshan qiladi-da, dil niyatlarini voqif etadi.
O‘shanda har kim o‘z ishiga yarasha
Xudodan tahsin oladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Korinfliklar 4:5</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='3' verse='20' id='J3v20-21'>
<text>Qabihlik qilgan odam nurdan nafratlanadi.
Qilmishlari fosh bo‘lmasligi uchun u nurdan qochadi.
Haqiqat yo‘lini tutgan odam esa nurga keladi.
Bunday odamning ishlari Xudo orqali qilinganligini
nur hammaga ayon qiladi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 3:20-21</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-10'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 10 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='12' verse='31' id='Ex12v31'>
<text>O‘sha tundayoq fir’avn Muso bilan Horunni
chaqirtirib aytdi:
— O‘zlaringiz ham, Isroil xalqingiz ham yo‘qolinglar!
Mening yurtimdan chiqib ketinglar!
O‘zlaringiz aytganingizday,
borib Egangizga sajda qilaveringlar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 12:31</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='13' verse='17' id='Act13v17'>
<text>Mana shu Isroil xalqining Xudosi
bizning ota–bobolarimizni tanlab oldi.
Ular Misrda musofir bo‘lib yashagan vaqt davomida
Xudo ulardan buyuk xalq yaratdi.
Buyuk qudrati bilan ularni Misrdan olib chiqdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylarning faoliyati 13:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-11'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 11 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='64' chapter='1' verse='13' id='3J1v13-14'>
<text>Senga aytadigan gapim ko‘p,
ammo ularni siyoh bilan qog‘ozga yozishni istamadim.
Undan ko‘ra, yaqin orada o‘zing bilan yuzma–yuz ko‘rishib
gaplashaman, deb umid qilaman.</text>
<ref>3 Yuhanno 13-14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='21' verse='25' id='J21v25'>
<intro>Havoriy Yuhanno yozgan:</intro>
<text>Iso yana ko‘p boshqa ishlar qilgan.
Bular birma–bir yozib chiqilganda edi,
yozilgan kitoblar olamga ham sig‘mas edi,
deb o‘ylayman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 21:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-12'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 12 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='22' chapter='3' verse='1' id='Ct3v1'>
<text>Kechqurun o‘rnimda yotganimda,
Butun qalbim bilan sevgan oshig‘imni qo‘msadim.
Juda qo‘msadim, lekin uni topolmadim.</text>
<ref>Sulaymonning go‘zal qo‘shig‘i 3</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='66' chapter='3' verse='20' id='Ap3v20'>
<text>Mana, Men eshik oldida turib,
taqillatyapman.
Kim ovozimni eshitib eshikni ochsa,
Men o‘shaning oldiga kiraman.
Men u bilan va u Men bilan ovqatni
baham ko‘ramiz.</text>
<ref>Injil, Vahiy 3:20</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-13'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 13 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='1' chapter='1' verse='27' id='Gn1v27-28'>
<text>Xudo O‘z suratiday qilib yaratdi inson zotini.
Erkagu ayol qilib yaratdi ularni.
Xudo insonlarga marhamat ko‘rsatib,
aytdi:
“Barakali bo‘lib, ko‘payinglar,
yer yuzini to‘ldirib, itoat ettiringlar.”</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Ibtido 1:27-28</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='7' verse='19' id='Mt7v19'>
<text>Yaxshi meva bermaydigan har bir daraxt
kesilib, olovga tashlanadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 7:19</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-14'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 14 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='42' verse='1' id='Is42v1'>
<text>Egam aytar: Mana Mening qulim,
O‘zim uni qo‘llab–quvvatlayman.
Men O‘zim uni tanlaganman.
Undan juda mamnunman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 42:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='50' chapter='2' verse='7' id='Ph2v7'>
<text>Iso Masih Xudoning tabiatiga ega edi,
shunda ham U Xudo bilan tengligini mahkam tutmadi.
Aksincha, U bu ulug‘vorlikdan voz kechib,
qul tabiatiga kirdi, inson bo‘lib tug‘ildi.</text>
<ref>Filipiliklar 2:7</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-15'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 15 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='42' chapter='22' verse='42' id='L22v42'>
<intro>Iso ibodat qilib dedi:</intro>
<text>Ey Ota! Qaniydi, bu azob kosasini Mendan uzoqlashtirsang!
Ammo Mening xohishim emas,
Sening xohishing bajo bo‘lsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Luqo 22:42</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='5' verse='8' id='H5v8'>
<text>Garchi Iso Xudoning O‘g‘li bo‘lsa ham,
azob–uqubat chekib, itoatkorlikning asl ma’nosini angladi.</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 5:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-16'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 16 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='44' verse='8' id='Is44v8'>
<text>Vahimaga tushmang, qo‘rqmang!
Sizga qadimdan e’lon qilib, bildirmadimmi?!
Sizlar Mening guvohlarimsiz!
Mendan boshqa xudo bormi?!
Yo‘q, boshqa qoya yo‘q.
Men boshqa hech birini bilmayman!</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Isha’yo 44:8</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='1' verse='8' id='Act1v8'>
<intro>Iso Masih havoriylarga dedi:</intro>
<text>Muqaddas Ruh sizlarni qamrab olganda,
kuch–qudratga to‘lasizlar.
Quddusda, Yahudiya va Samariyada,
yer yuzining hamma burchaklarida
sizlar Mening shohidlarim bo‘lasizlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 1:8</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-17'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 17 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='23' chapter='26' verse='16' id='Is26v16'>
<text>Ey Egamiz, kulfatda qolganlarida
Ular Senga yuz burdilar,
Sening tanqidlaring ostida egildilar.</text>
<ref>Yesha’yo 26:16</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='52' chapter='2' verse='2' id='1Th2v2'>
<intro>Havoriy Pavlus yozgan:</intro>
<text>Biz Filippi shahrida ko‘p azob chekkandik,
haqoratlarga uchragandik.
Ammo ko‘p qarshiliklarga qaramay,
Xudoning Xushxabarini sizga aytishimiz uchun
Uning O‘zi bizga jasorat berdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Salonikaliklar 2:2</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-18'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 18 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='27' chapter='3' verse='17' id='Dn3v17'>
<text>Shadrax, Meshax va Abednaxu shohga shunday javob berishdi:
Biz sig‘inadigan Xudo bizni olovli chuqurlikdan ham,
sizning qo‘lingizdan ham qutqarishga qodir.</text>
<ref>Doniel 3:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='58' chapter='13' verse='6' id='H13v6'>
<text>Biz ishonch bilan ayta olamiz:
“Egam Madadkorimdir, shu bois qo‘rqmayman.
Insonlar menga nima qila oladi? !”</text>
<ref>Ibroniylar 13:6</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-19'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 19 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='48' verse='15' id='Ps48v15'>
<text>Xudo o‘sha istehkomlarga o‘xshaydi.
U to abad bizning Xudoyimizdir,
U to abad bizning yo‘lboshchimiz bo‘ladi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 47:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='100' verse='5' id='Ps100v5'>
<text>Egamiz yaxshidir,
Uning sodiq sevgisi abadiy davom etadi,
Sadoqati esa barcha nasllarga o‘tadi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 99:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-20'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 20 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='24' chapter='21' verse='14' id='Jr21v14'>
<text>Men qilmishingizga yarasha jazoingizni beraman.
Egamizning kalomi shudir.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyo 21:14</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='63' chapter='1' verse='9' id='2J1v9'>
<text>Masih ta’limotini ortda qoldirib,
o‘zicha “jadallab ketgan” odamda Xudo yo‘q.
Masih ta’limoti bo‘yicha yashagan odamda esa Ota ham, O‘g‘il ham bor.</text>
<ref>2 Yuhanno 9</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-21'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 21 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='5' chapter='7' verse='6' id='Dt7v6'>
<text>Sizlar Egangiz Xudoning muqaddas xalqisiz.
U sizlarni yer yuzidagi jamiki xalqlar
orasidan O‘z xalqi,
O‘z xazinasi qilib tanlab oldi.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Qonun takrori 7:6</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='59' chapter='2' verse='5' id='Jc2v5'>
<text>Xudo bu dunyodagi kambag‘allarni imonda boy qilish uchun tanladi!
U O‘zini sevganlarga va’da qilganday,
ularga O‘z Shohligini meros qilib berdi.</text>
<ref>Yoqub 2:5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-22'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 22 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='2' chapter='23' verse='1' id='Ex23v1'>
<text>Yolg‘on xabarlar tarqatmanglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Misrdan chiqish 23:1</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='40' chapter='28' verse='15' id='Mt28v15'>
<text>Soqchilar pulni olib,
"Isoning jasadini o‘g‘irlab ketishdi",
degan firibni yoyadigan bo‘lishdi.
Voqeaning shu ta’rifi bugungi kungacha
yahudiylar orasida keng tarqalgan.</text>
<ref>Injil, Matto 28:15</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-23'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 23 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='11' chapter='18' verse='21' id='1Rg18v21'>
<text>Ilyos xalqning ro‘parasiga chiqib, ularga tanbeh berdi:
— Qachongacha ikki kemaning uchini tutib yurasizlar? !
Agar Egamiz Xudo bo‘lsa, Unga ergashinglar.
Bordi–yu, Baal Xudo bo‘lsa, unga sajda qilinglar.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 3 Shohlar 18:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='64' chapter='1' verse='11' id='3J1v11'>
<text>Aziz birodarim,
sen yomonlikka emas, yaxshilikka taqlid qil.
Yaxshilik qiluvchi odam Xudodandir.
Yomonlik qiluvchi esa Xudoni ko‘rmagan.</text>
<ref>Injil, 3 Yuhanno 11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-24'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 24 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='54' chapter='6' verse='17' id='1T6v17'>
<text>Bu dunyoda boylik topgan odamlarga
mag‘rurlanmaslikni va bevafo boylikka umid bog‘lamaslikni buyur.
Zavq olishimiz uchun har narsani
mo‘l-ko‘l ehson etgan barhayot Xudoga
umid bog‘lasinlar.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Timo‘tiy 6:17</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='25' chapter='3' verse='24' id='Thr3v24'>
<text>Qalbimda aytaman:
Egamdir mening bor–yo‘g‘im,
Shunday ekan, yolg‘iz Undadir mening umidim.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Yeremiyoning marsiyasi 3:24</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-25'>
<title>Kalom, Dushanba, 25 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='115' verse='13' id='Ps115v13'>
<text>Egamiz O‘zidan qo‘rqqanlarga baraka beradi,
Kattayu kichikka bir xilda baraka beradi.</text>
<ref>Zabur 113:21</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='44' chapter='10' verse='34' id='Act10v34-35'>
<text>Butrus ularga gapira boshladi:
— Haqiqatan ham, Xudo tarafkashlik qilmasligini bilaman.
Har bir elatda Xudodan qo‘rqadigan
va to‘g‘ri ishlarni qiladigan har bir odam Unga ma’quldir.</text>
<ref>Injil, Havoriylar 10:34-35</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-26'>
<title>Kalom, Seshanba, 26 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='12' chapter='19' verse='15' id='2Rg19v15'>
<text>Ey, ikki karub orasida taxt qurgan
Isroil xalqining Xudosi — Egamiz!
Butun yer yuzidagi shohliklarning
tanho Xudosi Sensan.
Osmonni va yerni Sen yaratgansan.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, 4 Shohlar 19:15</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='19' chapter='72' verse='11' id='Ps72v11'>
<text>Hamma shohlar unga ta’zim aylasin,
Hamma xalqlar unga xizmat qilsin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 71:11</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-27'>
<title>Kalom, Chorshanba, 27 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='5' verse='30' id='J5v30'>
<intro>Iso Masih dedi:</intro>
<text>Men O‘zimdan O‘zim hech narsa qilolmayman.
Otam Menga qanday aytsa, shunday hukm qilaman,
shuning uchun hukmim to‘g‘ridir.
Zotan, Men O‘z irodamni emas,
balki Meni yuborgan Otamning irodasini
bajo keltirishni istayman.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 5:30</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='2' verse='17' id='1J2v17'>
<text>Dunyo ham, uning nafsi ham o‘tib ketadi.
Xudoning irodasini bajargan odam esa abadiy yashaydi.</text>
<ref>1 Yuhanno 2:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-28'>
<title>Kalom, Payshanba, 28 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='11' verse='26' id='J11v26'>
<intro>Iso Masih aytgan:</intro>
<text>Kimda–kim Menga ishonib yashasa,
to abad o‘lmaydi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 11:26</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='62' chapter='2' verse='25' id='1J2v25'>
<text>Masihning O‘zi buni bizga va’da qilgan.
Bu abadiy hayotdir.</text>
<ref>Injil, 1 Yuhanno 2:25</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-29'>
<title>Kalom, Juma, 29 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='1' verse='6' id='J1v6-7'>
<text>Xudo Yahyo ismli bir odamni yubordi.
Yahyo Nur haqida shahodat qilgani kelgan edi,
toki hamma uning shahodati orqali
imon keltirsin.</text>
<ref>Injil, Yuhanno 1:6-7</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='45' chapter='10' verse='17' id='R10v17'>
<text>Imon tinglashdan,
ya’ni Masih haqidagi Xushxabarni eshitishdan
kelib chiqadi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Rimliklar 10:17</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-30'>
<title>Kalom, Shanba, 30 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='19' chapter='71' verse='9' id='Ps71v9'>
<text>Keksaygan chog‘imda meni tashlab qo‘ymagin,
Quvvatim ketganda, meni tark etmagin.</text>
<ref>Zabur 70:9</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='43' chapter='19' verse='26' id='J19v26-27'>
<text>Iso onasini va onasi yonida turgan sevikli shogirdini ko‘rdi.
Iso onasiga:
— Ona, mana bu sizning o‘g‘lingiz! — dedi. Keyin shogirdiga qarab:
— Mana bu sening onang! — dedi.
O‘sha vaqtdan boshlab u shogird Maryamni o‘z uyiga oldi.</text>
<ref>Yuhanno 19:26-27</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-12-31'>
<title>Kalom, Yakshanba, 31 Dekabr 2017</title>
<parol book='26' chapter='37' verse='12' id='Ez37v12'>
<text>Egamiz Rabbiy shunday demoqda:
Ey xalqim Isroil,
Men qabrlaringizni ochib,
sizlarni go‘rdan chiqaraman.
So‘ng sizlarni o‘z yurtingiz — Isroilga
qaytarib olib boraman.</text>
<ref>Tavrot, Hezeqil 37:12</ref>
</parol>
<parol book='49' chapter='2' verse='4' id='E2v4-5'>
<text>Mehr–shafqatga boy Xudo O‘zining bizga bo‘lgan
buyuk muhabbatini quyidagicha ko‘rsatdi:
Garchi biz gunohlarimiz tufayli ruhan o‘lik bo‘lsak ham,
Xudo bizni Masih bilan birga tiriltirdi.</text>
<ref>Injil, Efesliklar 2:4-5</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
</thewordfile>
